to%20save%20the%20deodar%20forests.%20It%20is%20estimated%20that%20the%20rains%20in%20August%20that%20were%20accompanied%20by%20landslides%20and%20flash%20floods%20led%20to%20the%20loss%20of%20nearly%201%2C000%20deodar%20trees.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20construction%20has%20only%20been%20allowed%20on%20land%20where%20there%20are%20no%20trees%20but%20the%20entire%20area%20is%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fhimachal%2Fdespite-rain-disaster-himachal-pradesh-opens-shimla-green-belts-for-fresh-constructions-552457%3F_gl%3D1*4t6ixb*_ga*MTgxNDE0ODE3Mi4xNjk2ODIyMTA1%5C%22%3Eheavily%20burdened%20with%20buildings%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20could%20pose%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20forests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20gave%20a%20nod%20to%20the%20SDP%20on%20May%203%20followed%20by%20the%20Cabinet%E2%80%99s%20approval%20on%20June%2019.%20However%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20had%20ordered%20that%20the%20notified%20SDP%20should%20be%20kept%20on%20hold%20till%20all%20objections%20were%20addressed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20study%20conducted%20in%202013%2C%20based%20on%20the%20Environmental%20Impact%20Assessment%20of%20the%20green%20belts%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthenewshimachal.com%2F2023%2F06%2Fgovernment-allows-construction-in-core-and-green-areas-of-shimla-environmentalists-raise-concerns-over-depletion-of-greenery%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erecommended%20a%20complete%20ban%20on%20construction%20activity%20in%20Shimla%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20report%20highlighted%20the%20rampant%20haphazard%20construction%2C%20portraying%20Shimla%E2%80%99s%20transformation%20from%20the%20%E2%80%9CQueen%20of%20Hills%E2%80%9D%20into%20an%20urban%20nightmare.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHeavy%20rains%20in%20July%20and%20August%20had%20wreaked%20havoc%20in%20multiple%20areas%20of%20Himacha