ast-popular-blind-employees-survey-approval-rating-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20a%20Blind%20survey%2C%20Nvidia's%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20received%20the%20highest%20approval%20rating%20of%2096%25%2C%20while%20Western%20Digital%20CEO%20David%20Goeckeler%20was%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20list%20at%200%25.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22htan%40insider.com%20(Huileng%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceo-most-least-popular-blind-employees-survey-approval-rating-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22J%26amp%3BK%20Admin%20Ignored%20Own%20Depts'%20Advice%20to%20Amend%20Multi-Crore%20Contract%20to%20Favour%20Private%20Co%3A%20IAS%20Officer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12125951%2FF76OrBQbIAAaSSf.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESrinagar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20administration%20headed%20by%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Manoj%20Sinha%20went%20against%20the%20advice%20of%20the%20finance%20and%20law%20departments%20and%20amended%20a%20multi-crore%20contract%20midway%20to%20favour%20a%20private%20insurance%20company%2C%20a%20letter%20by%20an%20IAS%20officer%20has%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20contract%20was%20signed%20between%20the%20State%20Health%20Agency%20(SHA)%2C%20the%20nodal%20department%20involved%20in%20rolling%20out%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri-Jan%20Arogya%20Yojna%20(PM-JAY)%20insurance%20scheme%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20and%20Bajaj%20Allianz%20General%20Insurance%20Company%2C%20on%20December%2026%2C%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20day%20later%2C%20on%20December%2027%2C%202020%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20Chief%20Secretary%20Dr%20Arun%20K.%20Mehta%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20Lakshya%20Mehta%2C%20was%20hired%20by%20the%20insurance%20company%20where%20he%20currently%20serves%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98Senior%20Executive%E2%80%99%2C%20according%20to%20his%20LinkedIn%20profile.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20insurance%20company%20sought%20to%20pull%20out%20of%20the%20contract%20in%20September%20next%20year%2C%20the%20SHA%20modified%20the%20contract%20by%20providing%20a%2015%25%20addendum%20to%20the%20existing%20policy%20without%20any%20legal%20backing.%20The%20%E2%80%98illegal%E2%80%99%20changes%20were%20regularised%20by%20the%20Administrative%20Council%20headed%20by%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Sinha%2C%20even%20though%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20finance%20and%20law%20departments%20objected%20to%20the%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20an%20activist%20flagged%20these%20alleged%20irregularities%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigations%2C%20the%20agency%20transferred%20the%20complaint%20after%20six%20months%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Anti-Corruption%20Bureau%20(ACB)%20whose%20director%20reports%20to%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%2C%20one%20of%20the%20alleged%20suspects%20in%20the%20purported%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20claims%20are%20part%20of%20a%20letter%20by%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Public%20Enterprises%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20and%201992%20IAS%20officer%2C%20Ashok%20Kumar%20Parmar%2C%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigations.%20The%20letter%20seeks%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdeeper%20probe%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20Insurance%20Regulatory%20and%20Development%20Authority%20of%20India%20(IRDA)%20and%20the%20CBI%20into%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjk-top-ias-officer-ashok-kumar-parmar-cbi-probe-jal-jeevan-mission%5C%22%3EJ%26amp%3BK%3A%20Why%20a%20Top%20IAS%20Officer%20Has%20Sought%20a%20CBI%20Probe%20Into%20the%20Flagship%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EParmar%2C%20who%20previously%20flagged%20the%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20implementation%20of%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%2C%20a%20centrally-sponsored%20scheme%2C%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20has%20also%20sought%20protection%20under%20the%20Whistleblowers%20Protection%20Act%2C%202014%20in%20his%20latest%20letter%20which%20is%20also%20marked%20to%20the%20Principal%20Secretary%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20in%20PMO%2C%20Cabinet%20Secretary%2C%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%2C%20Department%20of%20Personnel%20and%20Training%20and%20Chairman%2C%20IRDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20Yatish%20Yadav%2C%20the%20Media%20Advisor%20to%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%2C%20and%20also%20Chief%20Secretary%20Mehta%2C%20on%20the%20allegations%20of%20%E2%80%9Cabuse%20of%20official%20position%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20acts%E2%80%9D%20to%20%E2%80%9Cconfer%20undue%20benefit%E2%80%9D%20on%20a%20private%20firm%20linked%20to%20Mehta.%20This%20story%20will%20be%20updated%20as%20and%20when%20their%20responses%20are%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20top%20government%20official%20who%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20named%20said%20the%20government%20will%20hold%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20spokesperson%20could%20not%20be%20reached%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20PM-JAY%20insurance%20scheme%20is%20fully%20funded%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20in%20Ladakh%20while%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20local%20administration%20provides%2010%25%20funding%20support%20while%20the%20rest%20is%20borne%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Parmar%E2%80%99s%20letter%2C%20the%20State%20Health%20Agency%20(SHA)%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20Bajaj%20Allianz%20signed%20the%20three-year%20contract%20on%20December%2025%2C%202020%2C%20with%20a%20provision%20of%20annual%20review%20after%20two%20years%2C%20according%20to%20official%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EClause%209(A)%20of%20the%20contract%2C%20accessed%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20states%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20three%20year%20term%20of%20this%20insurance%20contract%20is%20subject%20to%20renewal%20after%20two%20years%20for%20one%20more%20year.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20September%202021%2C%20less%20than%20a%20year%20after%20the%20contract%20came%20into%20force%2C%20Bajaj%20Allianz%20sought%20to%20withdraw%2C%20reportedly%20citing%20losses.%20A%20top%20official%20of%20the%20administration%2C%20who%20is%20privy%20to%20the%20matter%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20insurance%20company%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20freedom%20to%20withdraw%20from%20the%20contract%20unless%20the%20SHA%20agreed%20in%20writing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20SHA%20never%20agreed%20to%20the%20plea%20in%20writing.%20Instead%2C%20it%20changed%20the%20contract%20into%20a%20full%20reimbursement%20contract%20on%20December%2025%2C%202021%20with%20a%20top%20up%20fee%20of%2015%25%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20official%20said%2C%20underlining%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20original%20contract%20happened%20as%20a%20part%20of%20tendering%20process%2C%20but%20the%20addendum%20was%20arbitrary.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInsurance%20companies%20cannot%20claim%20that%20they%20are%20running%20into%20a%20loss%20due%20to%20a%20particular%20insurance%20policy%20for%20J%26amp%3BK%20as%20that%20is%20what%20insurance%20is%20all%20about.%20Diversification%20leads%20to%20its%20viability.%20These%20claims%20and%20the%20SHA%20agreement%20in%20this%20particular%20contract%20has%20no%20basis%20in%20the%20insurance%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20official%20added%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20number%20of%20families%20was%20also%20%E2%80%9Cincreased%20by%201%2C087%2C108%20to%20provide%20more%20financial%20benefit%E2%80%9D%20to%20Bajaj%20Allianz.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20alleged%20scam%20happened%20between%20December%202021%20and%20April%202022%2C%20as%20per%20the%20modified%20agreement%2C%20and%20it%20has%20caused%20losses%20worth%20more%20than%20Rs%20500%20crore%20to%20the%20state%20exchequer%2C%20according%20to%20Parmar%E2%80%99s%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%20J%26amp%3BK%20government%20order%20(No.%2049-JK(GAD)%20of%202019%20Dated%3A%2019-11-2019)%2C%20fund%20authorisation%20in%20central%20and%20state%20schemes%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20having%20financial%20implication%20of%20more%20than%20Rs%2050%20crore%20need%20the%20approval%20of%20Chief%20Secretary%20Mehta.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20notification%20dated%20January%209%2C%202020%2C%20by%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20finance%20department%20states%20that%20projects%20above%20Rs%2020%20crore%20shall%20be%20green-lighted%20after%20the%20approval%20of%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Sinha.%20%E2%80%9CBoth%20the%20offices%20have%20to%20be%20in%20the%20loop%20on%20the%20matter.%20It%20is%20either%20pure%20incompetence%20or%20a%20criminal%20nexus%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20official%20quoted%20above%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20top%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%20official%2C%20rejecting%20the%20claims%20made%20by%20Parmar%20in%20his%20letter%20to%20the%20CBI%2C%20said%20that%20the%20policy%20was%20modified%20midway%20because%20Bajaj%20Allianz%20%E2%80%9Crefused%20to%20renew%E2%80%9D%20the%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNew%20contract%20would%20have%20taken%20perhaps%20three%20more%20months%20to%20finalise.%20During%20the%20intermediate%20period%2C%20an%20arrangement%20was%20made%20by%20the%20Health%20department%20as%20per%20General%20Finance%20Rules%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20official%20said%2C%20asking%20not%20to%20be%20quoted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20point%20to%20the%20rules%20under%20which%20the%20contract%20was%20modified%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20choice%20was%20between%20continuity%20of%20service%20or%20disruption.%20Calculations%20made%20by%20the%20health%20department%20show%20that%20the%20model%20they%20adopted%20(to%20provide%2015%25%20extra%20charge%20to%20Bajaj%20Allianz%20was%20least%20costly%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20official%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697096018000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12125951%2