e%2Farticleshow%2F104364790.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Licence%20of%20Company%20Whose%20Cough%20Syrups%20Were%20Linked%20to%20Deaths%20of%20Uzbek%20Kids%20Remains%20Cancelled%3A%20Officials%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F25160810%2Fpexels-cottonbro-studio-5858832.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20officials%20associated%20with%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20state%20drug%20control%20administration%20say%20the%20manufacturing%20licence%20of%20Marion%20Biotech%2C%20a%20Noida-based%20pharma%20firm%20whose%20cough%20syrup%20was%20linked%20to%20the%20deaths%20of%20more%20than%2060%20children%20in%20Uzbekistan%20last%20year%2C%20continues%20to%20remain%20cancelled%20as%20of%20now.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20licence%20of%20the%20company%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fuzbekistan-cough-syrup-noida-marion-biotech-mandaviya%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecancelled%20on%20December%2030%2C%202022%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20the%20Indian%20authorities%20as%20the%20Uzbekistan%20government%20found%20that%20Marion%20Biotech%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fspan%3E%20samples%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fwho-uzbekistan-cough-syrup-noida-product-alert%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98Dok1%20Max%20syrup%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Ambronol%20cough%20syrup%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20were%20contaminated%20with%20diethylene%20glycol%20(DEG)%20%E2%80%93%20an%20industrial%20solvent%20that%20is%20used%20as%20an%20antifreeze%20agent.%20According%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fnews%2Fitem%2F23-01-2023-who-urges-action-to-protect-children-from-contaminated-medicines%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWorld%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20it%20can%20be%20fatal%20even%20if%20consumed%20in%20small%20amounts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETalking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20late%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20October%2011%2C%20Noida%20drug%20inspector%20Vaibhav%20Babbar%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20company%E2%80%99s%20plant%20is%20not%20opened%20yet%20as%20the%20%5Blicence%5D%20cancellation%20order%20prevails.%E2%80%9D%20Asked%20again%2C%20he%20reiterated%20that%20the%20order%20%E2%80%9Csustains%20as%20of%20now%20and%20there%20is%20no%20ambiguity%20in%20that%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20further%20information%2C%20he%20redirected%20this%20correspondent%20to%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20head%20of%20drug%20control%20administration%2C%20Shashi%20Mohan%20Gupta.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGupta%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20company%20has%20not%20even%20submitted%20the%20corrective%20and%20preventive%20actions%20(CAPA)%20plan.%20So%20how%20can%20we%20even%20think%20of%20deliberating%20on%20revoking%20the%20cancellation%20order%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia%2Findia-allows-cough-syrup-firm-linked-uzbek-deaths-re-open-factory-document-2023-10-11%2F%5C%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20on%20September%2014%2C%20Gupta%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20no%20known%20case%20of%20a%20lack%20of%20quality%20in%20other%20medicines%20manufactured%20by%20the%20firm.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTherefore%2C%20in%20view%20of%20natural%20justice%2C%20the%20appeal%20of%20the%20manufacturing%20firm%20is%20partially%20accepted.%20Its%20permission%20to%20make%20products%20using%20(cough%20syrup%20ingredient)%20propylene%20glycol%20is%20cancelled%2C%20and%20it%20is%20allowed%20to%20make%20and%20sell%20all%20other%20products%2C%E2%80%9D%20Reuters%20quoted%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20September%20statement%20as%20saying%2C%20on%20October%2011.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Findia-drug-impurities-fight%5C%22%3EInside%20the%20Fight%20To%20Decide%20How%20Pure%20India%E2%80%99s%20Drugs%20Need%20To%20Be%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20talking%20to%20The%20Wire%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20he%20did%20not%20comment%20on%20the%20statement%2C%20but%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20licence%20of%20the%20entire%20plant%20remains%20cancelled%20%5Band%20as%20such%20it%20can%E2%80%99t%20manufacture%20%3Cem%3Eany%3C%2Fem%3E%20drug%5D%20and%20we%20haven%E2%80%99t%20deliberated%20anything%20upon%20its%20reopening%20since%20the%20CAPA%20plan%20has%20not%20been%20submitted%20by%20the%20company%2C%20yet.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20CAPA%20plan%20is%20sent%20%5Bto%20us%5D%2C%20it%20would%20be%20forwarded%20to%20the%20Drug%20Controller%20General%20of%20India%2C%20Rajeev%20Raghuvanshi%2C%20for%20evaluation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%20Gupta%20also%20told%20Reuters%20on%20October%2011%20that%20Raghuvanshi%20had%20asked%20the%20company%20to%20submit%20the%20said%20plan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECAPA%20is%20a%20set%20of%20guidelines%20that%20a%20pharma%20firm%20commits%20to%20following%20once%20it%20has%20been%20found%20violating%20good%20manufacturing%20practices%20in%20an%20investigation%20carried%20out%20by%20drug%20regulatory%20authorities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20said%20plan%2C%20the%20company%20lists%20out%20the%20series%20of%20steps%20it%20would%20undertake%20to%20avoid%20repeating%20the%20violations.%20Once%20the%20plan%20is%20submitted%20to%20the%20regulatory%20authorities%2C%20they%20evaluate%20it%20and%20take%20a%20decision%20on%20its%20suitability%2C%20accordingly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%2C%20in%20March%202023%2C%20three%20people%20associated%20with%20the%20firm%20were%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fuzbekistan-child-deaths-three-of-noida-based-firm-arrested-for-contaminated-medicines%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Earrested%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eby%20the%20Noida%20police%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20investigation%20done%20by%20drug%20control%20authorities.%20Marion%20Biotech%E2%80%99s%20owner%20was%20also%20named%20in%20the%20FIR.%20Asked%20about%20his%20status%2C%20the%20UP%20drug%20controller%20said%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20far%20as%20my%C2%A0%20limited%20knowledge%20goes%2C%20he%20got%20a%20stay%20%5Bon%20arrest%5D%20from%20a%20court.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20may%20be%20mentioned%20here%20that%20while%20the%20WHO%20had%20linked%20drugs%20of%20several%20companies%20based%20in%20India%20with%20deaths%20of%20children%20due%20to%20the%20presence%20of%20DEG%20in%20their%20respective%20products%2C%20it%20was%20only%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Marion%20Biotech%20that%20the%20government%20of%20India%20was%20also%20able%20to%20establish%20the%20contamination%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20lab%20investigations.%20In%20no%20other%20such%20instance%20did%20the%20investigation%20in%20India%20establish%20the%20contamination.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fwith-officials-rarely-checking-for-impurities-indias-drug-testing-has-a-big-blind-spot%5C%22%3EWith%20Officials%20Rarely%20Checking%20for%20Impurities%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20Drug%20Testing%20Has%20a%20Big%20Blind%20Spot%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUsually%2C%20DEG%20ends%20up%20entering%20these%20drugs%20through%20an%20ingredient%20called%20propylene%20glycol%20(PG)%2C%20which%20is%20added%20to%20syrups%20to%20make%20them%20soluble.%20However%2C%20either%20due%20to%20oversight%2C%20or%20to%20cut%20costs%2C%20pharma%20companies%20end%20up%20using%20PG-mixed%20DG.%20In%20case%20of%20oversight%2C%20they%20often%20don%E2%80%99t%20test%20PG%20for%20any%20impurities%2C%20before%20production%20%E2%80%93%20which%20they%20are%20supposed%20to.%20In%20an%20earlier%20instance%2C%20Marion%20Biotech%E2%80%99s%20Tuhin%20Bhattacharya%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Finvestigates%2Fspecial-report%2Fhealth-coughsyrup-india%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EReuters%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20his%20firms%20had%20sold%20drugs%20without%20checking%20PG%20for%20impurities%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697095773000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F25160810%2Fpexels-cottonbro-studio-5858832.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fmarion-biotech-licence-cough-syrup-uzbek-kids-remains-cancelled%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20report%20had%20said%20that%20barring%20cough%20syrups%2C%20Marion%20Biotech%20would%20be%20allowed%20to%20manufacture%20other%20products%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0provided%20it%20submitted%20the%20corrective%20and%20preventive%20actions%20plan.%20The%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20state%20drug%20controller%20told%20The%20Wire%20that%20the%20company%20has%20not%20yet%20submitted%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fmarion-biotech-licence-cough-syrup-uzbek-kids-remains-cancelled%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Akshay%3A%20Would%20skip%20meal%20to%20save%20money%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697095686000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104364392%2Cimgsize-55242.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fakshay-kumar-recalls-staying-in-a-house-with-rs-100-rent-says-we-would-miss-our-meal-in-the-morning-to-save-money-for-the-ticket%2Farticleshow%2F104364392.cms%22%2C%22summary%2