r%20summer%2C%20Chris%2C%20he%20thought%20that%20we%20were%20getting%20a%20divorce.%20So%20he%20called%20me%20and%20basically%20he%20was%20like%2C%20%E2%80%98I'd%20love%20to%20take%20you%20out.'%20And%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%E2%80%98What%20do%20you%20mean%3F'%20He%20was%20like%2C%20%E2%80%98Well%2C%20aren't%20you%20and%20Will%20getting%20a%20divorce%3F'%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%E2%80%98No.%20Chris%2C%20those%20are%20just%20rumours.'%20He%20was%20appalled.%20And%20he%20profusely%20apologized%20and%20that%20was%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeople.com%2Fjada-pinkett-smith-says-chris-rock-asked-her-out-on-a-date-amid-rumors-she-and-will-were-divorcing-exclusive-8349420%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPeople%20Magazine%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20interview%20comes%20ahead%20of%20the%20release%20of%20Ms%20Pinkett%20Smith's%20forthcoming%20memoir%2C%20%E2%80%9CWorthy%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20releases%20on%20October%2017.%20It%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20Chris%20Rock%20or%20his%20team%20has%20not%20yet%20responded%20to%20the%20same.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJada%20Pinkett%20Smith%20and%20Will%20Smith%20got%20married%20in%201997%20and%20share%20two%20children%2C%2024-year-old%20son%20Jaden%20Smith%20and%2021-year-old%20daughter%20Willow%20Smith.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20made%20news%20last%20year%20after%20Will%20Smith%20slapped%20Chris%20Rock%20during%20the%20Oscars%202022%20%C2%A0shouting%20%26quot%3Bkeep%20my%20wife's%20name%20out%20of%20your%20f***ing%20mouth%26quot%3B.%20Mr%20Rock%20had%20joked%20about%20Jada%20Pinkett%20and%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BCan't%20wait%20for%20GI%20Jane%202%2C%26quot%3B%20referring%20to%20her%20hair.%20It%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20she%20has%20a%20condition%20called%20alopecia%20which%20causes%20hair%20loss.%20The%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Pursuit%20of%20Happyness%E2%80%9D%20actor%20later%20apologised%20to%20both%20Mr%20Rock%20and%20the%20Academy%20for%20his%20behaviour.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20Instagram%20post%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20publicly%20apologize%20to%20you%2C%20Chris.%20I%20was%20out%20of%20line%20and%20I%20was%20wrong.%20I%20am%20embarrassed%20and%20my%20actions%20were%20not%20indicative%20of%20the%20man%20I%20want%20to%20be.%20There%20is%20no%20place%20for%20violence%20in%20a%20world%20of%20love%20and%20kindness.%E2%80%9D%20He%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BViolence%20in%20all%20of%20its%20forms%20is%20poisonous%20and%20destructive.%20My%20behaviour%20at%20last%20night's%20Academy%20Awards%20was%20unacceptable%20and%20inexcusable.%20Jokes%20at%20my%20expense%20are%20a%20part%20of%20the%20job%2C%20but%20a%20joke%20about%20Jada's%20medical%20condition%20was%20too%20much%20for%20me%20to%20bear%20and%20I%20reacted%20emotionally.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Pinkett%20Smith%20told%20People%20Magazine%20in%20an%20interview%20that%20at%20first%2C%20she%20assumed%20it%20was%20a%20staged%20joke.%20%26quot%3BIt%20wasn't%20until%20Will%20started%20to%20walk%20back%20to%20his%20chair%20that%20I%20even%20realised%20it%20wasn't%20a%20skit.%20I'm%20going%20to%20be%20by%20his%20side%20but%20also%20allow%20him%20to%20have%20to%20figure%20this%20out%20for%20himself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697094540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fmqh066k_will-smith-jada-_625x300_12_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fjada-pinkett-smith-says-chris-rock-asked-her-out-amid-marriage-trouble-with-will-smith-4473755%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jada%20Pinkett%20Smith%20and%20Will%20Smith%20got%20married%20in%201997%20and%20share%20two%20children%2C%2024-year-old%20son%20Jaden%20Smith%20and%2021-year-old%20daughter%20Willow%20Smith.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fjada-pinkett-smith-says-chris-rock-asked-her-out-amid-marriage-trouble-with-will-smith-4473755%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fjada-pinkett-smith-says-chris-rock-asked-her-out-amid-marriage-trouble-with-will-smith-4473755%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fjada-pinkett-smith-says-chris-rock-asked-her-out-amid-marriage-trouble-with-will-smith-4473755%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Global%20Leadership%20Is%20Not%20Just%20About%20Drafting%20a%20Statement%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22165508%2FH20230909138364.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20not%20attending%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20party%20at%20the%20G-20%20summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20effectively%20signalled%20that%20the%20group%20no%20longer%20matters%20in%20geo-economic%20and%20geo-political%20terms.%20What%20matters%20is%20the%20G-7%20and%20its%20direct%20competitor%20BRICS.%20And%20if%20the%20South%20African%20edition%20of%20BRICS%20is%20the%20sign%20of%20times%20to%20come%2C%20then%20this%20is%20where%20the%20world%20is%20converging.%20However%2C%20to%20convey%20China%E2%80%99s%20core%20message%20to%20the%20world%20that%20it%20favours%20globalisation%2C%20it%20sent%20Premier%20Li%20Qiang%20to%20attend%20the%20G-20%20summit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProtocol%20could%20be%20another%20reason%20why%20Xi%20may%20have%20decided%20to%20miss%20the%20Delhi%20jamboree%20since%20Modi%20would%20have%20given%20exceptional%20attention%20to%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%20Moreover%2C%20to%20communicate%20that%20bilateral%20ties%20were%20at%20an%20all-time%20low%2C%20Xi%20did%20not%20bother%20to%20personally%20convey%20his%20absence%20to%20the%20Indian%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EExcept%20for%20the%20US%2C%20all%20nations%20believe%20that%20the%20world%20is%20moving%20towards%20multipolarity%20with%20two%20overarching%20global%20visions%20led%20by%20the%20US%20and%20China%20respectively.%20Therefore%2C%20so%20long%20as%20they%20are%20not%20pushed%20to%20choose%20between%20the%20two%20visions%2C%20nations%20are%20hopeful%20of%20drawing%20benefits%20from%20both.%20What%20is%20underplayed%20is%20the%20reality%20that%20global%20prosperity%20ultimately%20hinges%20on%20the%20success%20of%20the%20fourth%20industrial%20revolution%20underpinned%20by%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20(AI).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F21222939%2FPresident_Biden_met_with_President_Xi_of_the_PRC_before_the_2022_G20_Bali_Summit.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F21222939%2FPresident_Biden_met_with_President_Xi_of_the_PRC_before_the_2022_G20_Bali_Summit.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F21222939%2FPresident_Biden_met_with_President_Xi_of_the_PRC_before_the_2022_G20_Bali_Summit-300x149.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-659470%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22508%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20shakes%20hands%20with%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20G20%20leaders%E2%80%99%20summit%20in%20Bali%2C%20Indonesia%2C%20November%2014%2C%202022.%20Photo%3A%20White%20House%2FWikimedia%20Commons%2C%20Public%20domain%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20software%20driven%20revolution%20with%20its%20competing%20standards%2C%20rules%2C%20norms%2C%20and%20regulations%20for%20the%20two%20visions%20will%20compel%20the%20nations%20to%20choose%20between%20them%20for%20digital%20commerce%2C%20trade%2C%20and%20navigation.%20And%20this%20may%20happen%20as%20early%20as%202030.%20In%20geopolitical%20terms%2C%20this%20means%20that%20unless%20the%20US%20endorses%20globalisation%20in%20totality%20(trade%2C%20commerce%2C%20and%20especially%20technology%2C%20which%20is%20unlikely)%2C%20early%20signs%20of%20bipolarity%20fragmented%20between%20the%20two%20visions%20may%20emerge%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20decade.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%2C%20which%20is%20a%20key%20geopolitical%20pivot%20in%20the%20Asia%20Pacific%20%E2%80%93%20where%20the%20two%20visions%20will%20play%20out%20%E2%80%93%20has%20chosen%20to%20align%20itself%20with%20the%20US%20vision.%20Moreover%2C%20unwilling%20to%20adjust%20with%20the%20risen%20(not%20rising%20or%20emerging)%20China%2C%20India%20has%20picked%20competition%20over%20cooperation%20with%20Beijing%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20Asia%20Society%20India%20on%20September%2013%2C%202022%2C%20external%20affairs%20minister%2C%20S.%20Jaishankar%20said%20that%20a%20multi-polar%20Asia%20is%20necessary%20for%20the%20Asian%20century%20and%20multi-polar%20world%2C%20implying%20that%20India%20and%20China%20are%20equal%20poles%20in%20Asia%20and%20the%20world.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20251px)%2085vw%2C%20251px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12102237%2F51TTL0Br3L._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-196x300.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22251%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12102237%2F51TTL0Br3L._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-196x300.jpg%20196w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12102237%2F51TTL0Br3L._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%20654w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-679616%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22384%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EZbigniew%20Brzezinski%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Grand%20Chessboard%3C%2Fem%3E%20(1997)%20published%20by%20Basic%20Books.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJaishankar%20has%20clearly%20not%20read%20or%20understood%20Zbigniew%20Brzezinski%E2%80%99s%20book%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Grand%20Chessboard%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ewhich%20is%20a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Efascinating%20treatise%20on%20global%20strategy.%20According%20to%20Brzezinski%2C%20geo-strategic%20players%20are%20those%20nations%20which%20have%20the%20capability%2C%20capacity%20and%20political%20will%20to%20influence%20events%20beyond%20their%20borders.%20The%20US%2C%20China%2C%20and%20Russia%20fall%20in%20this%20category%20as%20distinct%20from%20major%20powers%20like%20Germany%2C%20France%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20Japan%20and%20the%20like.%20Thus%2C%20all%20geostrategic%20powers%20are%20major%20powers%2C%20but%20all%20major%20powers%20are%20not%20geostrategic%20players.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EInterestingly%2C%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20world%2C%20major%20powers%20should%20be%20assessed%20by%20their%20technological%20prowess%20(as%20the%20fourth%20industrial%20revolution%20builds%20on%20the%20third%20revolution).%20This%20is%20central%20to%20both%20economic%20and%20military%20power.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBased%20on%20power%20in%20the%20field%20of%20technology%20%E2%80%93%20AI%20and%20emerging%20technologies%20which%20converge%20into%20it%20%E2%80%93%20India%20is%20not%20in%20the%20global%20game.%20Yet%2C%20being%20a%20significant%20geopolitical%20pivot%2C%20whose%20importance%20is%20derived%20not%20by%20its%20national%20power%2C%20but%20by%20its%20sensitive%20location%2C%20India%20is%20being%20courted%20by%20all%20three%20geostrategic%20players.%20Besides%20its%20geography%2C%20which%20sits%20astride%20the%203%2C000%20nautical%20miles%20sea%20lanes%20of%20communication%20from%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20to%20the%20Strait%20of%20Malacca%20%E2%80%93%20through%20which%20China%E2%80%99s%20four%20trillion%20dollars%20trade%20passes%20annually%20%E2%80%93%20India%20is%20also%20a%20huge%20market%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20added%20attractions%20for%20the%20US%20are%20India%E2%80%99s%20massive%2C%20disciplined%20military%3B%20it%20being%20the%20biggest%20arms%20importer%20in%20the%20world%3B%20and%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20belief%20that%20a%20tight%20US%20embrace%20will%20help%20it%20to%20compete%20in%20the%20region%20with%20China.%20Before%20discussing%20why%20India%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20as%20it%20is%20evolving%20may%20end%20up%20being%20a%20dangerous%20self-goal%2C%20there%20is%20need%20to%20understand%20the%20two%20global%20visions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ETwo%20global%20visions%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20US%20vision%20seeks%20a%20replay%20of%20the%20Cold%20War%20where%20containment%20of%20the%20Soviet%20sphere%20of%20influence%20(politically%20and%20militarily)%20by%20deterrence%2C%20without%20a%20direct%20war%20between%20the%20two%20blocs%2C%20eventually%20led%20to%20the%20USSR%E2%80%99s%20demise%20along%20with%20the%20Warsaw%20Pact%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20US%20created%20the%20Bretton%20Woods%20institutions%20%E2%80%93%20the%20World%20Bank%20and%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20%E2%80%93%20for%20global%20economic%20integration.%20It%20dominated%20the%20world%20by%20its%20exceptional%20military-industrial%20complex%2C%20established%20some%20760%20military%20bases%20across%20the%20globe%2C%20led%20the%20military-technological%20revolution%2C%20and%20ushered%20in%20the%20third%20industrial%20revolution%2C%20pivoted%20on%20chips%20and%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20unipolar%20scenario%2C%20from%201991%20to%202017%2C%20the%20US%20ruled%20the%20world%20based%20on%20its%20military%20and%20dollar%20dominance.%20It%20toppled%20governments%20through%20colour%20revolutions%2C%20wars%2C%20and%20sanctions%20to%20propagate%20a%20hegemony%20that%20sought%20to%20build%20a%20world%20in%20which%20its%20corporations%20and%20military%20would%20have%20full%20freedom.%20Its%20official%20ideology%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20democracy%20and%20human%20rights%2C%20but%20these%20were%20mostly%20expedient%20slogans%20to%20further%20Washington%E2%80%99s%20global%20interests.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJust%20as%20the%20US%20was%20fighting%20small%20wars%2C%20especially%20in%20Afghanistan%20and%20Iraq%2C%20by%202010%2C%20it%20realised%20that%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Liberation%20Army%20(PLA)%20could%20match%20the%20US%20military%20in%20the%20west%20Pacific.%20The%20PLA%20had%20operational%20systems%20and%20guided%20munitions%20that%2C%20it%20noted%2C%20were%20as%20capable%20as%20its%20own.%20The%20PLA%20could%20close%20the%20kill%20chain%20as%20quickly%20as%20the%20US%20military.%20It%20could%20also%20conduct%20stand-off%20precision%20attacks%20at%20long%20ranges%20as%20well%20as%20the%20US%20military%20with%20its%20indigenous%20mortars%2C%20rockets%2C%20missiles%2C%20and%20artillery%20projectiles%20most%20of%20which%20were%20guided.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECoupled%20with%20miniaturisation%2C%20guided%20weapons%20brought%20unprecedented%20lethality%20at%20long%20ranges.%20This%20led%20the%20Pentagon%20to%20announce%20the%20third%20offset%20strategy%20driven%20by%20AI%20and%20autonomy%20in%202014.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIncidentally%2C%20China%20announced%20its%20One%20Belt%20One%20Road%20(or%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative)%20project%20in%202013%20followed%20by%20the%20Digital%20Silk%20Road%20in%202015.%20With%20expertise%20in%20destroying%20nations%20but%20none%20in%20building%20them%2C%20the%20US%20was%20at%20sea%20in%20the%20face%20of%20numerous%20challenges%20presented%20by%20China%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EIts%20exceptional%20capability%20and%20capacity%20in%20international%20infrastructure%20building%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3Edeep%20pockets%20to%20fund%20the%20BRI%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3Emilitary%20capability%20in%20the%20domains%20of%20space%2C%20cyber%2C%20and%20electromagnetic%20spectrum%2C%20and%20land-based%20missiles%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3Eits%20intense%20integration%20with%20the%20world%20economy%20whereby%20China%20was%20the%20major%20trading%20partner%20of%20over%20140%20nations%20and%20regions%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3Eit%20being%20the%20largest%20global%20manufacturer%20and%20trader%20in%20goods.%20This%20made%20terms%20like%20decoupling%2C%20de-risking%2C%20and%20diversifying%20difficult%20to%20carry%20through%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3Eits%20exceptional%20civil-military%20fusion%20for%20developing%20AI%20ecosystem%2C%20and%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3Eits%20ability%20to%20commercialise%20AI%20incubated%20in%20the%20US%20(Silicon%20Valley).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20AI%20is%20built%20and%20not%20bought%20off%20the%20shelf%2C%20China%2C%20by%202017%2C%20could%20lead%20the%20US%20in%20three%20of%20the%20six%20stacks%20which%20comprise%20AI.%20While%20lagging%20behind%20the%20US%20in%20AI%20hardware%2C%20software%2C%20and%20human%20resources%2C%20China%20excelled%20in%20data%20management%2C%20applications%20(for%20commercialisation)%2C%20and%20integration%20or%20Internet%20of%20Things%20(IoT%2C%20also%20called%20internet%20modules).%20This%20started%20a%20tech%20war%20with%20the%20Trump%20administration%20banning%20Huawei%205G%20in%202018%20followed%20by%20denial%20of%C2%A0%20chips%2C%20chip-making%20design%20software%20and%20tools%20to%20China%20by%20the%20Biden%20administration.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12102642%2Fbri_map.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22780%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12102642%2Fbri_map.png%20780w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12102642%2Fbri_map-300x169.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-679620%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBelt%20and%20Road%20Initiative.%20Photo%3A%20World%20Bank%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnable%20to%20match%20China%E2%80%99s%20BRI%2C%20the%20US%20started%20maligning%20it%20by%20calling%20it%20a%20%E2%80%98debt%20trap%E2%80%99%2C%20underplaying%20the%20fact%20that%20138%20nations%20from%20the%20Global%20South%20were%20on%20board.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20US%20with%20its%20G7%20partners%20also%20dabbled%20in%20half-baked%20connectivity%20projects%20like%20Build-Back-Better-World%2C%20Global%20Gateway%2C%20and%20recently%20the%20Indian-Middle%20East-Europe%20project%20unveiled%20at%20the%20G20%20summit%20in%20India.%20These%20projects%2C%20if%20they%20ever%20fructify%2C%20will%20likely%20supplement%20the%20BRI%20rather%20than%20challenge%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Biden%20administration%20decided%20to%20double%20down%20on%20its%20own%20strength%20by%20turning%20the%20Obama%20administration%E2%80%99s%202011%20%E2%80%98pivot%20to%20Asia%E2%80%99%20policy%20into%20%E2%80%98integrated%20deterrence%E2%80%99%20by%20aligning%20allies%2C%20strategic%20partners%20(India)%20and%20the%20Atlantic-specific%20NATO%20into%20its%20Indo-Pacific%20defence%20network.%20It%20was%20lost%20on%20the%20US%20that%20there%20is%20no%20military%20answer%20to%20the%20BRI%3A%20a%20strategy%20built%20on%20expansion%20of%20commerce%2C%20trade%20and%20navigation%20by%20connectivity%2C%20AI%2C%20and%20big%20data.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20the%20US%20continues%20to%20be%20driven%20by%20containment%20and%20global%20domination%2C%20China%20speaks%20about%20%E2%80%98global%20respect%E2%80%99.%20It%20asks%20that%20nations%20onboard%20the%20BRI%20framework%20%E2%80%93%20which%20includes%20the%20SCO%20and%20the%20Russia-led%20Eurasian%20Economic%20Union%20nations%20%E2%80%93%20remain%20sensitive%20to%20China%E2%80%99s%20interests%20while%20framing%20their%20foreign%20policy.%20To%20achieve%20this%20vision%2C%20China%20has%20enunciated%20what%20it%20terms%20its%20Global%20Development%20Initiative%20(GDI)%2C%20Global%20Security%20Initiative%20(GSI)%2C%20and%20Global%20Civilisation%20Initiative%20(GCI)%20concepts%2C%20working%20under%20the%20United%20Nations%20umbrella.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAligned%20with%20the%20UN%E2%80%99s%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%20(SDGs)%20for%202030%2C%20GDI%20is%20expected%20to%20create%20green%2C%20efficient%2C%20and%20cost-effective%20development%20given%20China%E2%80%99s%20lead%20in%20Lithium-ion%20batteries%2C%20solar%20batteries%2C%20and%20new%20energy%20vehicles%20through%20BRI%20which%20will%20offer%20a%20mix%20of%20physical%2C%20mobile%2C%20and%20digital%20economies%20to%20the%20Global%20South%20nations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20mobile%20economy%2C%20whose%20inflection%20point%20in%20China%20came%20in%202014%2C%20is%20about%20mobile%20internet%2C%204G%20networks%20with%20consumers%20in%20the%20lead.%20This%20mobile%20economy%20with%20imported%20hardware%20was%20offered%20to%20the%20world%20recently%20by%20India%20as%20a%20highpoint%20of%20its%20G-20%20presidency.%20Moreover%2C%20since%20China%20has%20a%20lead%20over%20the%20G7%20nations%20in%20rolling%20out%20a%205G%20network%2C%20the%20inflection%20point%20for%20a%20digital%20economy%20based%20on%20AI%2C%20data%2C%20cloud%2C%20and%20blockchain%20came%20in%202017%20in%20China.%20The%20digital%20economy%20led%20by%20enterprises%20is%20about%20the%20industrial%20internet%20where%2C%20given%20China%E2%80%99s%20expertise%20in%20software%2C%20it%20is%20ahead%20in%20the%20internet%20module%20or%20IoT.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFast%20forward%20to%20some%20possible%20scenarios%2C%20three%20to%20five%20years%20from%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELarge%20Language%20Models%20(LLMs)%20like%20Chat%20GPT-4%2C%20which%20took%20the%20world%20by%20storm%20in%202023%20by%20its%20generative%20AI%2C%20will%20be%20hundreds%20of%20times%20larger%20with%20exceptional%20capabilities.%20Instead%20of%20generating%20text%2C%20the%20new%20LLMs%20will%20be%20able%20to%20generate%20sequences%20of%20actions%20to%20be%20done%20and%20then%20be%20able%20to%20do%20them%20by%20itself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiven%20its%20lead%20in%20the%20industrial%20internet%20on%20account%20of%205G%20availability%20at%20scale%2C%20China%20will%20likely%20focus%20its%20LLMs%20not%20on%20Natural%20Language%20Processing%20(NLP)%20to%20generate%20text%2C%20videos%2C%20and%20images%20like%20Chat%20GPT%2C%20but%20on%20the%20SDGs%20underpinning%20the%20GDI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20example%2C%20since%20the%20LLMs%20will%20be%20able%20to%20generate%20AI%20which%20could%20communicate%20and%20negotiate%20with%20humans%20on%20the%20phone%20and%20interact%20with%20other%20AIs%20to%20ensure%20glitches%20in%20supply%20chains%20are%20removed%20quickly%2C%20they%20will%20have%20tremendous%20uses%20in%20health%20services%2C%20smart%20logistics%2C%20smart%20cities%2C%20digital%20finances%2C%20biotechnology%2C%20and%20other%20applications%20of%20the%20fourth%20industrial%20revolution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELLMs%20will%20also%20have%20a%20big%20role%20in%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20metaverse%20or%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20the%20internet.%20The%20convergence%20of%20virtual%20reality%20and%20a%20digital%20second%20life%20(avatars)%20will%20be%20boosted%20by%20generative%20AI%20for%20business%20models%2C%20trade%2C%20and%20commerce.%20Thus%2C%20the%20technology%20layer%20underpinning%20the%20metaverse%20will%20comprise%20AR%2FVR%20(Augmented%20Reality%2FVirtual%20Reality)%2C%20IoT%2C%205G%2C%206G%2C%20and%20mesh%20network%20which%20self-organise%20and%20self-configure%20nodes%20for%20efficiently%20routing%20data%20to%20and%20from%20clients.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-and-china-are-trapped-in-a-conflict-of-their-own-making%5C%22%3EIndia%20and%20China%20are%20Trapped%20in%20a%20Conflict%20of%20Their%20Own%20Making%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20the%20above%2C%20two%20things%20become%20clear%20%E2%80%93%20one%2C%20the%20need%20for%20cyber%20security%20against%20backdoor%20and%20adversarial%20attacks%2C%20and%20second%2C%20to%20set%20standards%2C%20norms%2C%20regulations%2C%20and%20roles%20for%20new%20technologies%20of%20the%20fourth%20industrial%20revolution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20US%20is%20determined%20to%20obstruct%20China%E2%80%99s%20innovations%2C%20the%20tech%20war%20started%20by%20the%20US%20will%20intensify.%20This%20is%20likely%20to%20result%20in%20the%20splintering%20of%20the%20internet%20and%20eventually%20fragmentation%20of%20industrial%20supply%20chains%20for%20trade%20and%20commerce.%20Given%20this%2C%20it%20will%20become%20increasingly%20difficult%20for%20nations%20aligned%20with%20the%20two%20global%20visions%20to%20trade%20with%20one%20another%20digitally.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFurthermore%2C%20most%20Global%20South%20nations%20have%20been%20attracted%20by%20GSI%20whose%20basic%20premise%20is%20indivisible%20security%2C%20implying%20a%20no%20zero-sum%20game%20or%20one%E2%80%99s%20security%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20another%E2%80%99s%20security.%20Simply%20put%2C%20instead%20of%20absolute%20security%2C%20nations%20should%20consider%20relative%20security.%20GSI%20also%20advocates%20an%20end%20to%20unilateral%20sanctions%20(outside%20the%20UN)%20and%20bloc%20confrontation%2C%20as%20well%20as%20non-interference%20in%20the%20internal%20affairs%20of%20other%20nations.%20It%20also%20advocates%20respect%20for%20each%20nation%E2%80%99s%20traditions%20and%20values%20%E2%80%93%20as%20against%20the%20instrumentalist%20%E2%80%98universal%20values%E2%80%99%20for%20human%20rights%2C%20democracy%2C%20and%20empowerment%20which%2C%20as%20we%20noted%2C%20the%20US%20pursues%20only%20selectively.%20In%20a%20fast-fragmenting%20world%2C%20all%20nations%2C%20especially%20big%20ones%20like%20India%2C%20will%20have%20to%20choose%20a%20side.%20%E2%80%98Balancing%E2%80%99%20may%20no%20longer%20be%20an%20option.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThus%2C%20senior%20Indian%20analysts%E2%80%99%20contention%20that%20India%20should%20remain%20engaged%20with%20BRICS%2C%20the%20SCO%2C%20QUAD%2C%20and%20the%20G-7%20nations%20as%20this%20would%20increase%20its%20diplomatic%20options%20in%20a%20polarised%20world%20is%20not%20sustainable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EG-20%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20presidency%20of%20the%20G-20%20summit%20will%20be%20remembered%20for%20two%20things.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%2C%20the%20absence%20of%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20and%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%2C%20whose%20nation%E2%80%99s%20economies%2C%20according%20to%20IMF%202023%20figures%2C%20grew%20faster%20than%20any%20other%20G-7%20nation.%20After%20the%20spectacular%20success%20of%20the%20BRICS%202023%20summit%20in%20Johannesburg%2C%20the%20answer%20to%20US%E2%80%99%20dollar%20dominance%20was%20found%20in%20trading%20in%20local%20currency%20and%20BRICS%20Pay%20(this%20will%20not%20replace%2C%20but%20displace%20SWIFT)%2C%20an%20electronic%20banking%20system%20which%20Iran%20will%20join%20in%20January%202024%20amongst%20other%20nations.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20inclusion%20of%20the%20African%20Union%20as%20the%20new%20G-20%20member%20was%20a%20pyrrhic%20victory%20compared%20with%20the%20six%20new%20members%20added%20to%20the%20BRICS%20(these%20include%20all%20global%20major%20energy%20exporters%20and%20importers)%20given%20that%2050%20of%20the%2054%20African%20nations%20attended%20the%202023%20BRICS%20summit.%20With%20%24300%20billion%20annual%20trade%2C%20China%20is%20the%20largest%20trading%20partner%20of%20the%20African%20continent%20and%20Russia%20is%20the%20biggest%20arms%20exporter.%20Thus%2C%20while%20China%20is%20the%20undisputed%20leader%20of%20Global%20South%2C%20to%20humour%20India%2C%20the%20US%20and%20G-7%20have%20endorsed%20it%20as%20the%20voice%20of%20Global%20South.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F10175233%2FF5pyX8ua4AAoHu2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F10175233%2FF5pyX8ua4AAoHu2.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F10175233%2FF5pyX8ua4AAoHu2-300x97.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F10175233%2FF5pyX8ua4AAoHu2-1024x329.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-672418%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22386%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EG20%20Summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20Sunday%2C%20September%2010.%20Photo%3A%20%40narendramodi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESecond%2C%20the%20Delhi%20G-20%20joint%20declaration%20was%20made%20possible%20not%20because%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20foresight%20or%20India%E2%80%99s%20exceptional%20negotiating%20skills%20but%20because%20India%20is%20a%20major%20geopolitical%20pivot%20wooed%20by%20the%20US%2C%20and%20not%20yet%20abandoned%20by%20China%20and%20Russia.%20The%20Delhi%20declaration%20was%20a%20watered-down%20version%20of%20the%20Bali%20G-20%20declaration%20since%20for%20the%20US%2C%20the%20bilateral%20Modi-Biden%20meeting%20before%20the%20official%20G-20%20summit%20was%20far%20more%20important%20that%20the%20joint%20statement%20which%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20reality%20of%20the%20Ukraine%20war.%20Modi%20had%20one-on-one%20meetings%20with%20most%20G-7%20nations%20since%20they%2C%20like%20the%20US%2C%20have%20stakes%20in%20the%20Indo%20Pacific%20region%20which%20may%20be%20decisive%20factors%20in%20global%20geopolitics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiven%20the%C2%A0%20US%E2%80%99s%20support%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20G-20%2C%20which%20comes%20close%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20general%20election%20in%202024%2C%20it%20would%20be%20natural%20for%20Biden%20to%20want%20a%20quick%20execution%20of%20the%20joint%20declaration%20signed%20during%20the%20Indian%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20the%20US%20in%20June.%20Washington%20does%20not%20want%20India%20to%20go%20the%20Australia%20way%2C%20which%2C%20while%20being%20a%20member%20of%20both%20QUAD%20and%20AUKUS%2C%20is%20now%20busy%20improving%20its%20trade%20ties%20with%20China%2C%20or%20like%20Malaysia%20which%20has%20decided%20to%20downplay%20China%E2%80%99s%20new%20map%20which%20infringes%20its%20sovereignty%2C%20in%20favour%20of%20improving%20prospects%20for%20trade%20with%20China.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20gambles%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20silence%20on%20China%2C%20despite%20cozying%20up%20to%20the%20US%2C%20will%20have%20its%20limits%20if%20really%20pushed%20to%20the%20brink.%20Ever%20since%20the%20Galwan%20episode%20in%20June%202020%2C%20India%20has%20gone%20quiet%20on%20even%20its%20other%20neighbour%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20with%20it%20not%20making%20its%20usual%20appearance%20in%20election%20rhetoric.%20With%20a%20tendency%20to%20see%20everything%20through%20a%20prism%20of%20its%20domestic%20audience%2C%20China%20and%20Pakistan%20being%20aligned%20poses%20a%20graver%20challenge%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20politics%20than%20is%20acknowledged.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20good%20geopolitics%20is%20and%20should%20be%20rooted%20in%20geography%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20statecraft%20should%20concentrate%20on%20decent%20relations%20with%20Pakistan%20and%20China.%20If%20India%20was%20honest%20with%20itself%2C%20it%20would%20know%20that%20PLA%E2%80%99s%20April%202020%20incursions%20into%20Ladakh%20were%C2%A0%20the%20consequence%20of%20India%20creating%20a%20new%20map%20after%20the%20revocation%20of%20Article%20370%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20on%C2%A0%20August%205%2C%202019)%20which%20resulted%20in%20a%C2%A0%20Union%20Territory%20(UT)%20status%20for%20Ladakh.%20Conscious%20of%20this%20fact%2C%20and%20China%E2%80%99s%20displeasure%2C%20external%20affairs%20minister%20Jaishankar%20travelled%20to%20Beijing%20on%20August%2011%2C%202019%20to%20explain%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20new%20map%20would%20not%20change%20the%20reality%20on%20the%20ground.%20China%20rejected%20his%20explanation%20and%20changed%20reality%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESadly%2C%20the%20Indian%20military%20(medium%20power)%20risks%20being%20outflanked%20by%20the%20PLA%E2%80%99s%20(major%20power)%20in%20case%20of%20a%20confrontation%20and%20this%20challenge%20has%20three%20dimensions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%2C%20as%20against%20the%20Indian%20military%2C%20which%20will%20wage%20combat%20across%20physical%20battle%20spaces%20comprising%20land%2C%20air%2C%20and%20sea%20domains%2C%20the%20PLA%20will%20likely%20engage%20four%20battles%20paces.%20Its%20physical%20battle-space%20will%20comprise%20land%2C%20air%2C%20sea%2C%20outer%20space%2C%20and%20near-space%20(for%20hypersonic%20missiles)%20domains.%20The%20virtual%20battle-space%20will%20include%20cyberspace%20and%20the%20electromagnetic%20spectrum.%20The%20information%20battle-space%20will%20have%20wired%20and%20wireless%20networks%20through%20which%20data%20passes.%20And%20the%20cognition%20battle%20space%20%E2%80%93%20where%20an%20information%20war%20will%20be%20unleashed%20%E2%80%93%20will%20involve%20a%20mind%20war%2C%20which%20will%20entail%20assaulting%20the%20enemy%E2%80%99s%20judgement.%20The%20PLA%20is%20likely%20to%20emphasise%20cognitive%20confrontation%20and%20push%20to%20seek%20an%20early%20cognitive%20victory.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%2C%20unlike%20the%20Indian%20military%2C%20the%20war%20fought%20by%20the%20PLA%20will%20not%20be%20confined%20to%20a%20battlefield%20or%20combat%20space.%20And%20three%2C%20China%20will%20not%20fight%20a%20tactical%20war%20at%20the%20frontline%20where%20the%20Indian%20army%20has%20an%20advantage%2C%20but%20across%20the%20entire%20combat%20zone%20at%20the%20operational%20level%20where%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20war%20will%20be%20decided.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiven%20all%20this%2C%20never%20has%20it%20been%20more%20critical%20for%20India%20to%20improve%20relations%20with%20its%20neighbour%2C%20China.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20about%20tactics%2C%20but%20about%20being%20on%20the%20right%20side%20of%20history.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPravin%20Sawhney%E2%80%99s%20recent%20book%20is%C2%A0The%20Last%20War%3A%20How%20AI%20Will%20Shape%20India%E2%80%99s%20Final%20Showdown%20With%20China%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697094004000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22165508%2FH20230909138364.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fglobal-leadership-is-not-just-about-drafting-a-statement%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Based%20on%20its%20achievements%20in%20key%20