rty%20that%20has%20an%20upper%20hand%20in%20the%20state%20polls%20will%20be%20rewarded%20with%20a%20charged%20cadre%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20a%20head%20start%20ahead%20of%20the%20grand%20finale.%20To%20use%20a%20cricket%20analogy%2C%20the%20party%20that%20wins%20this%20round%20will%20go%20into%20the%20finals%20(2024)%20in%20good%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20elections%20have%20an%20interesting%20history.%20History%20doesn't%20repeat%20itself%20but%20it%20does%20rhyme.%20In%202003%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%20all%20the%20three%20states%20-%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20-%20but%20went%20on%20to%20lose%20the%20general%20election%20in%202004.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202008%2C%20the%20BJP%20retained%20two%20states%2C%20losing%20Rajasthan%2C%20but%20went%20on%20again%20to%20lose%20the%20general%20elections%20in%202009.%20In%202013%2C%20the%20BJP%20again%20won%20all%20three%20and%20went%20on%20to%20win%20a%20historic%20mandate%20in%202014.%20In%202018%2C%20BJP%20lost%20all%20four%20states%2C%20including%20Telangana%2C%20but%20went%20on%20to%20win%20big%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EElections%20are%20a%20lot%20about%20creating%20a%20buzz%20-%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3Bmahaul%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20-%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20party.%20With%2012%25%20to%2015%25%20voters%20finally%20deciding%20to%20vote%20on%20polling%20day%2C%20according%20to%20CSDS%20post%20poll%20studies%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Emahaul%3C%2Fem%3E%20impacts%20these%20late%20deciders.%20The%20BJP%20is%20in%20power%20in%20only%20one%20of%20the%20five%20states%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20The%20Congress%20is%20in%20power%20in%20two%20states%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20and%20regional%20parties%20BRS%20and%20MNF%20are%20in%20power%20in%20Telangana%20and%20Mizoram.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20create%20any%20positive%20environment%20in%20their%20favour%2C%20the%20Congress%20will%20need%20to%20win%20a%20minimum%20of%20three%20states%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%2C%20a%20minimum%20of%20two%20states.%20Regional%20forces%2C%20to%20remain%20relevant%20in%20southern%20and%20northeastern%20India%20during%20the%20national%20election%2C%20will%20need%20to%20retain%20Telangana%20and%20Mizoram.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOpinion%20polls%20predict%20a%20tight%20race%20now%20in%20all%20states%2C%20and%20are%20throwing%20up%20mixed%20results.%20The%20message%20that%20is%20clear%20is%20that%20the%20incumbents%20will%20not%20have%20it%20easy%20and%20will%20need%20to%20slog%20to%20retain%20power.%20These%20highly%20localised%20polls%20are%20turning%20into%20a%20seat-by-seat%20election%2C%20which%20makes%20the%20task%20difficult%20for%20pollsters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarly%20opinion%20polls%20have%20to%20be%20taken%20with%20a%20pinch%20of%20salt%2C%20as%20not%20all%20major%20parties%20have%20declared%20candidates.%20Local%20faces%20are%20important%20in%20state%20polls%2C%20and%20the%20main%20voting%20consideration%20for%2039%25%20voters.%20Party%20is%20the%20decider%20for%2035%25%20and%20for%2021%25%20voters%2C%20the%20leadership%20is%20critical%2C%20per%20the%20CSDS%20post-poll%20study%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20contenders%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20Congress%2C%20are%20adopting%20different%20strategies%20in%20different%20states%2C%20also%20highlighting%20caution%20and%20confusion%20in%20both%20camps.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20sticking%20to%20its%20successful%20strategy%20in%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20era%20in%20states%20where%20it%20is%20in%20the%20opposition%2C%20has%20not%20declared%20a%20Chief%20Minister%20face%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Telangana.%20It%20has%20opted%20for%20a%20combined%20leadership%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20surprisingly%2C%20it%20is%20shying%20away%20even%20from%20projecting%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20as%20its%20face%20in%20the%20only%20state%20where%20it%20is%20in%20power%2C%20opting%20for%20combined%20leadership.%20This%20plan%20didn't%20work%20well%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20declared%20Kamal%20Nath%20as%20its%20presumptive%20chief%20minister%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20to%20make%20it%20a%20presidential-style%20contest%20taking%20advantage%20of%20a%20weaker%20Shivraj%20Chouhan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20whenever%20the%20Congress%20defeated%20the%20BJP%20while%20being%20in%20the%20opposition%20-%20Himachal%20(2022)%2C%20Karnataka%20(2023)%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20(2018)%20-%20it%20hadn't%20declared%20a%20chief%20minister%20face.%20In%20Telangana%2C%20it%20is%20going%20ahead%20with%20this%20tried%20and%20tested%20model%20of%20no%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Rajasthan%2C%20like%20the%20BJP%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20not%20officially%20declared%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20as%20its%20chief%20minister%20face.%20It%20is%20a%20move%20possibly%20to%20pacify%20Sachin%20Pilot%2C%20but%20Gehlot%20is%20all%20over%20posters.%20In%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20while%20the%20party%20is%20contesting%20under%20combined%20leadership%20of%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20and%20TS%20Singh%20Deo%2C%20Baghel%20is%20clearly%20the%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20hesitation%20in%20announcing%20the%20incumbent%20Chief%20Minister%20as%20the%20face%20of%20the%20party%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20the%20Congress's%20reluctance%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20cannot%20sit%20well%20with%20voters.%20How%20can%20voters%20trust%20these%20leaders%20when%20their%20parties%20don't%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Telangana%2C%20K%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%20or%20KCR%20is%20clearly%20the%20chief%20ministerial%20face%20of%20the%20BRS.%20There%20are%20questions%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20KCR%20eventually%20handing%20power%20to%20his%20son%20KT%20Rama%20Rao%20(KTR)%2C%20if%20the%20party%20wins.%20This%20has%20led%20to%20rumblings%20within%20the%20party's%20senior%20leadership%2C%20resulting%20in%20an%20exodus%20towards%20Congress%20and%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20been%20able%20to%20drive%20the%20narrative%2C%20to%20some%20extent%2C%20that%20the%20BRS-AIMIM-BJP%20are%20hand-in-glove%20with%20each%20other%20and%20this%20could%20help%20the%20party%20prevent%20a%20split%20in%20the%20opposition%20vote.%20A%20hung%20assembly%20situation%20is%20not%20ruled%20out%20per%20CVoter%20survey%2C%20with%20the%20BJP%20claiming%20to%20play%20kingmaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20learning%20from%20its%20losses%20in%20Himachal%20and%20Karnataka%2C%20has%20decided%20to%20release%20its%20candidates'%20list%20early.%20So%20far%2C%20it%20has%20named%2060%25%20candidates%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%2020%25%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20all%20but%20five%20seats%20in%20Chhattisgarh.%20The%20BRS%20too%20has%20released%20a%20candidates'%20list%20for%20almost%20all%20the%20seats.%20The%20Congress%20list%20is%20also%20expected%20post%20%3Cem%3Epitru%20paksha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20released%20its%20first%20list%20for%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20in%202018%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20November%2C%20just%20three%20weeks%20before%20polling.%20This%20is%20a%20big%20departure%20for%20a%20party%20that%20used%20to%20ask%20voters%20to%20ignore%20candidates%20and%20vote%20in%20the%20name%20of%20PM%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20also%20fielding%20many%20MPs%20in%20all%20these%20states%20to%20test%20their%20popularity%20ahead%20of%202024%20elections%2C%20pushing%20them%20to%20win%20seats%20it%20had%20lost%20in%202018%20elections.%20The%20party%20hopes%20such%20high%20profile%20candidates%20can%20rub%20off%20on%20surrounding%20seats%20and%20spur%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%20is%20banking%20on%20its%20successful%20guarantees%20model%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Karnataka%2C%20which%20includes%20cash%20doles%20to%20women%20and%20unemployed%20youth%2C%20free%20electricity%2C%20farm%20loan%20waivers%20and%20implementation%20of%20the%20Old%20Pension%20Scheme%20(OPS).%20It%20is%20trying%20to%20pitch%20its%20%3Cem%3Elaabharthi%20%3C%2Fem%3Emodel%20versus%20the%20BJP's%2C%20making%20it%20a%20current%20(Modi's%20central%20schemes)%20versus%20future%20%3Cem%3Elaabharti%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebattle.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Mizoram%2C%20the%20battle%20has%20become%20triangular%20with%20the%20entry%20of%20ZPM.%20The%20elections%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20impacted%20by%20the%20situation%20in%20neighbouring%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnemployment%2C%20price%20rise%20and%20corruption%20are%20the%20top%20three%20issues%20across%20states%20and%20could%20well%20decide%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20state%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697093460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-04%2Fvnlcq1no_voting-generic-reuters_625x300_18_April_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2F2023-state-polls-last-big-test-before-2024-4471350%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Though%20state%20and%20national%20elections%20are%20fought%20on%20different%20issues%20and%20have%20different%20context%2C%20all%20eyes%20will%20be%20on%20these%20polls%20that%20will%20be%20held%20four%20months%20before%20the%20general%20election%2C%20starting%20April.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2F2023-state-polls-last-big-test-before-2024-4471350%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2F2023-state-polls-last-big-test-before-2024-4471350%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2F2023-state-polls-last-big-test-before-2024-4471350%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Katrina%20gets%20into%20combat%20mode%20for%20Tiger%203%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697093410000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104363259%2Cimgsize-49694.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkatrina-kaif-launches-fierce-combat-mode-for-tiger-3-exclusive%2Farticleshow%2F104363327.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104363327.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EKatrina%20Kaif's%20character%20Zoya%20in%20%26quot%3BTiger%203%26quot%3B%20undergoes%20significant%20changes%2C%20with%20more%20intense%20combat%20scenes%2C%20leading%20to%20her%20specialized%20look%20resembling%20iconic%20action%20heroines.%20The%20film%2C%20directed%20by%20Maneesh%20Sharma%2C%20is%20set%20for%20a%20Diwali%20release.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Jigar%20Shah%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkatrina-kaif-launches-fierce-combat-mode-for-tiger-3-exclusive%2Farticleshow%2F104363327.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Signs%20That%20Israel%20Planning%20%26quot%3BSomething%20Big%26quot%3B%2C%20Weighing%20Gaza%20Ground%20Assault%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20troops%20are%20massing%20for%20what's%20widely%20seen%20as%20all%20but%20inevitable%3A%20a%20ground%20invasion%20of%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20public%20and%20the%20national%20security%20establishment%20in%20Israel%20are%20demanding%20retribution%20for%20the%20attacks%20by%20Hamas%20militants%20that%20claimed%20more%20than%201%2C000%20Israeli%20lives%20over%20the%20weekend.%20But%20a%20ground%20invasion%20would%20be%20complicated%20by%20Gaza's%20dense%20population%2C%20its%20complex%20underground%20network%20of%20tunnels%20and%20the%20danger%20it%20would%20pose%20to%20Israelis%2C%20Americans%20and%20others%20being%20held%20hostage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20is%20that%20it's%20basically%20house-to-house%20fighting%20once%20you%20get%20into%20Gaza.%20And%20so%20it%20could%20be%20a%20heavy%20price%2C%26quot%3B%20former%20US%20Defense%20Secretary%20and%20CIA%20Director%20Leon%20Panetta%20said%20Tuesday%20on%20Bloomberg%20Television's%20%26quot%3BBalance%20of%20Power.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BBut%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20very%20clear%20that%20Israel%20has%20made%20the%20decision%20that%20they%20have%20got%20to%20crush%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20invasion%20would%20bring%20heavy%20casualties%20on%20both%20sides%20and%20questions%20about%20whether%20Israel%20can%20devise%20an%20exit%20strategy%20for%20the%20conflict.%20It%20would%20also%20create%20ripple%20effects%20through%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20endangering%20Israel's%20fragile%20rapprochement%20with%20its%20Arab%20neighbors%20and%20increasing%20the%20risks%20that%20the%20conflict%20spirals%20into%20a%20broader%20regional%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20follows%20an%20invasion%2C%20a%20US%20official%20said%2C%20may%20resemble%20the%202004%20battle%20for%20Fallujah%20in%20Iraq%2C%20which%20involved%20bloody%20street-to-street%20fighting.%20Resistance%20in%20Gaza%20may%20be%20formidable%2C%20especially%20if%20neighboring%20countries%20provide%20reinforcements%2C%20according%20to%20the%20official%2C%20who%20discussed%20the%20sensitive%20matter%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20hasn't%20announced%20that%20it%20will%20send%20troops%20into%20Gaza%2C%20but%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20has%20promised%20that%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20we%20will%20do%20to%20our%20enemies%20in%20the%20coming%20days%20will%20reverberate%20with%20them%20for%20generations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDevelopments%20on%20the%20ground%20also%20suggest%20Israel%20is%20planning%20something%20big.%20It's%20bombarding%20Gaza%20from%20the%20air%2C%20land%20and%20sea.%20Its%20military%20is%20building%20a%20base%20next%20to%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20to%20accommodate%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20soldiers%20as%20columns%20of%20Israeli%20tanks%20move%20toward%20the%20region.%20The%20country%20has%20already%20mobilized%20300%2C000%20reservists%20%E2%80%94%20the%20most%20in%20its%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIsrael%20is%20going%20to%20respond%20very%20severely%20and%20aggressively%20and%20there%20will%20be%20more%20loss%20of%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Richard%20Hecht%2C%20a%20spokesman%20for%20the%20Israeli%20military%2C%20told%20journalists%20Tuesday.%3Cbr%3E%20Underground%20Stockpiles%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20growing%20conviction%20that%20Israel%20will%20launch%20a%20ground%20invasion%20rests%20on%20the%20limitations%20of%20aerial%20warfare%20in%20Gaza.%20Airstrikes%20are%20unlikely%20to%20succeed%20in%20clearing%20out%20the%20tunnels%2C%20underground%20weapons%20stockpiles%20and%20smuggling%20routes%20that%20made%20Saturday's%20attack%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20some%20point%20they're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20go%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Keith%20Alexander%2C%20a%20retired%20four-star%20US%20Army%20general%20who%20was%20director%20of%20the%20National%20Security%20Agency.%20%26quot%3BThey%20can%20do%20limited%20operations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20that's%20a%20fairly%20big%20area%20to%20occupy%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20to%20cover.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStreet-to-street%20fighting%20in%20Gaza%2C%20where%20two%20million%20residents%20are%20packed%20into%20an%20area%20just%20over%20twice%20the%20size%20of%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20would%20likely%20result%20in%20heavy%20civilian%20casualties.%20Arab%20officials%20fear%20images%20of%20dead%20civilians%20could%20prompt%20a%20backlash%20among%20Arab%20publics%2C%20putting%20pressure%20on%20their%20governments%20to%20cool%20ties%20with%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20longer%20the%20occupation%20lasts%2C%20the%20more%20ebbing%20of%20support%20that%20you'll%20see%20for%20Israel%20and%20the%20more%20pressure%20you'll%20see%20on%20Arab%20states%20from%20their%20publics%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20William%20Usher%2C%20a%20former%20Senior%20Intelligence%20Service%20officer%20at%20the%20Central%20Intelligence%20Agency%20who%20specializes%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%20%26quot%3BThis%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20devolve%20into%20a%20political%20and%20PR%20disaster.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEndangered%20Hostages%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThen%20there's%20the%20chilling%20complication%20of%20Hamas's%20hostages.%20During%20Saturday's%20raid%2C%20the%20group%20took%20scores%20of%20Israeli%20and%20foreign%20prisoners%2C%20from%20toddlers%20to%20elderly%20women.%20Hamas%20has%20said%20it's%20prepared%20to%20kill%20a%20hostage%20each%20time%20Israel%20strikes%20civilian%20homes%20in%20Gaza%20without%20warning.%20Their%20potential%20fate%20in%20any%20ground%20incursion%20is%20unknown.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20a%20serious%20risk%20of%20escalation.%20Israel%20has%20already%20seen%20rocket%20attacks%20from%20Lebanon%2C%20raising%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20multifront%20war%20and%20a%20descent%20into%20broader%20regional%20conflict%20if%20Israel%20responds%20with%20military%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHanging%20above%20all%20of%20this%20is%20the%20possibility%20of%20Iran%20being%20drawn%20in.%20%26quot%3BThe%20massacre%20and%20mass%20killing%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%20will%20bring%20a%20greater%20calamity%26quot%3B%20on%20Israel%2C%20Iran's%20Supreme%20Leader%20Ali%20Khamenei%20said%20at%20a%20ceremony%20on%20Tuesday.%20US%20generals%20have%20warned%20Iran%20not%20to%20get%20involved%20and%20sent%20a%20carrier%20strike%20group%20to%20the%20region%20to%20deter%20Tehran.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20the%20problem%20of%20what%20would%20follow%20an%20invasion.%20There's%20no%20guarantee%20of%20a%20durable%20political%20solution%20to%20accompany%20military%20action.%20Israel%20withdrew%20ground%20troops%20from%20Gaza%20in%202005%20in%20part%20because%20a%20previous%20occupation%20of%20the%20region%20proved%20too%20costly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20end%20will%20be%20when%20they%20accept%20an%20arrangement%20in%20which%20they%20give%20up%20any%20idea%20of%20carrying%20out%20terror%20attacks%20in%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20Yossi%20Kuperwasser%2C%20a%20former%20top%20Israeli%20military%20intelligence%20official%2C%20said%20of%20the%20militants.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20Israeli%20population%20understood%20what%20it%20means%20to%20live%20next%20to%20Hamas%2C%20they%20are%20ready%20to%20pay%20almost%20any%20price%20in%20order%20to%20stop%20living%20next%20to%20Hamas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697093400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fpllud3d8_idf-soldiers-guard-gaza-bloomberg_625x300_12_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdifficult-options-ahead-as-israel-weighs-ground-assault-on-gaza-strip-4473409%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israeli%20troops%20are%20massing%20for%20what's%20widely%20seen%20as%20all%20but%20inevitable%3A%20a%20ground%20invasion%20of%20Gaza.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdifficult-options-ahead-as-israel-weighs-ground-assault-on-gaza-strip-4473409%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdifficult-options-ahead-as-israel-weighs-ground-assault-on-gaza-strip-4473409%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdifficult-options-ahead-as-israel-weighs-ground-assault-on-gaza-strip-4473409%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nasir%2C%20Junaid%20Burnt%20on%20the%20Advice%20of%20'Senior'%20Vigilantes%2C%20Reveals%20Prime%20Accused%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F16225727%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-02-16-at-8.59.38-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3ENasir%20and%20Junaid%2C%20who%20were%20killed%20on%20the%20suspicion%20of%20cattle%20smuggling%2C%20were%20burnt%20by%20the%20accused%20after%20they%20were%20advised%20by%20%E2%80%9Csenior%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cinfluential%E2%80%9D%20cow%20vigilantes%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhow-violent-cow-vigilantism-made-monu-manesar-an-icon%5C%22%3EMonu%20Manesar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Tribune%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fharyana%2Finfluential-vigilantes-ordered-burning-of-nasir-junaid-bodies-552526%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20quoting%20Anil%20Multhan%2C%20one%20of%20the%20eight%20accused%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20accused%20kidnapped%20the%20duo%2C%20they%20brutally%20thrashed%20them%20and%20handed%20them%20over%20to%20Ferozepur%20Jhirka%20police%20in%20Haryana%2C%20who%20turned%20them%20away.%20They%20did%20not%20intend%20to%20kill%20the%20duo%2C%20said%20Multhan%2C%20but%20the%20physical%20assault%20committed%20against%20them%20went%20out%20of%20hand%2C%20resulting%20in%20their%20death.%20At%20this%20stage%2C%20the%20accused%20reached%20out%20to%20cow%20vigilantes%20over%20the%20phone%20and%20WhatsApp%20and%20were%20advised%20to%20burn%20the%20bodies%20to%20destroy%20forensic%20evidence%20and%20to%20weaken%20the%20case%20in%20court%2C%20Multan%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMulthan%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20in%20Gurugram%2C%20is%20in%20the%20custody%20of%20the%20Deeg%20police%20till%20October%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20officer%20from%20Rajasthan%20Police%20confirmed%20Multan%E2%80%99s%20version.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20burnt%20the%20bodies%20after%20much%20deliberations%20with%20some%20of%20the%20most%20celebrated%20faces%20of%20vigilantism.%20They%20had%20not%20anticipated%20the%20consequences%20of%20the%20thrashing%20and%20panicked.%20They%20could%20see%20both%20dying%2C%20and%20that%20is%20when%20they%20contacted%20the%20vigilantes%20of%20Haryana%20for%20guidance.%20They%20decided%20to%20burn%20the%20bodies%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20forensic%20evidence%20was%20left.%20We%20are%20probing%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20role%20of%20these%20vigilantes%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20official%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fharyana%2Finfluential-vigilantes-ordered-burning-of-nasir-junaid-bodies-552526%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3ETribune%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fground-report-how-junaid-and-nasir-were-killed-by-cow-vigilantes%5C%22%3EGround%20Report%3A%20How%20Junaid%20and%20Nasir%20Were%20Killed%20by%20%E2%80%98Cow%20Vigilantes%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Multan%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcow-vigilantes-extort-money-from-cattle-smugglers-alleges-key-accused-in-nasir-junaid-murder-case%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20cow%20vigilantes%20in%20Haryana%20and%20Rajasthan%20have%20been%20extorting%20money%20from%20cattle%20smugglers%20to%20allow%20them%20safe%20passage%20through%20the%20states.%20These%20vigilantes%20ran%20a%20close-knit%20group%20and%20tracked%20the%20movement%20of%20smugglers%20and%20trucks%20carrying%20cattle.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMultan%E2%80%99s%20statements%20highlight%20that%20these%20groups%20closely%20monitored%20smuggler%20activities%20and%20demanded%20payments%20from%20them.%20Failure%20to%20pay%20often%20resulted%20in%20violence%20and%20police%20intervention.%20It%20is%20this%20extortion%20money%20that%20helped%20these%20groups%20to%20fund%20their%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CExtortion%20is%20the%20key%20source%20of%20income%20of%20these%20gangs.%20They%20have%20a%20strong%20network%20in%20Mewat.%20They%20have%20lists%20of%20cattle%20smugglers%20and%20seek%20payment%20from%20them%20for%20allowing%20their%20trucks%20to%20pass%20through%20the%20area.%20If%20they%20fail%20to%20pay%2C%20they%20are%20thrashed%20and%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20police%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20went%20on%20to%20add%20that%20the%20payments%20depended%20on%20the%20number%20and%20type%20of%20cattle%20being%20smuggled%20and%20the%20area%20they%20were%20caught.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENasir%20and%20Junaid%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Multhan%2C%20earned%20the%20wrath%20of%20the%20accused%20for%20helping%20smugglers%20pass%20through%20the%20area%20without%20paying%20the%20extortion%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20plan%20of%20the%20accused%20was%20to%20catch%20the%20duo%20red-handed%20and%20then%20hand%20them%20over%20to%20the%20police%2C%20they%20could%20not%20do%20so%20as%20they%20could%20not%20get%20hold%20of%20the%20truck%20smuggling%20cattle.%20It%20was%20then%20the%20accused%20thrashed%20them%2C%20according%20to%20the%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20Multan%20in%20custody%2C%20Rajasthan%20Police%20expect%20him%20to%20reveal%20more%20about%20the%20case%20as%20well%20as%20the%20cow%20vigilantism%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20killing%20of%20the%20duo%20has%20become%20a%20major%20political%20issue%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20which%20is%20going%20to%20polls%20next%20month.%20It%20is%20expected%20to%20dominate%20electoral%20discourse%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20Mewat%20region%2C%20which%20comprises%20Alwar%2C%20Deeg%2C%20and%20Bharatpur%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20daily%2C%20there%20have%20been%20protests%20in%20the%20region%20against%20Rajasthan%20Police%20handing%20over%20Monu%20Manesar%20to%20Haryana%20Police.%20Manesar%2C%20who%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmonu-manesar-arrested-by-haryana-police-sit%5C%22%3Earrested%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Haryana%20Police%20in%20connection%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fharyana-violence-mewat-hate-and-provocative-videos%5C%22%3Eviolence%20in%20Nuh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20Rajasthan%20Police.%20He%20was%20then%20taken%20into%20Haryana%20Police%20custody%20on%20October%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Rajasthan%20Police%20is%20also%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20other%20accused%20in%20the%20Nasir-Junaid%20murder%20case.%20It%20is%20expected%20to%20hand%20over%20a%20list%20of%20cow%20vigilantes%20to%20the%20Haryana%20Police%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697093119000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F16225727%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-02-16-at-8.59.38-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnasir-junaid-burnt-on-the-advice-of-senior-vigilantes-reveals-prime-accused%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20accused%20said%20they%20wanted%20to%20thrash%20the%20duo%20and%20hand%20them%20over%20to%20police%2C%20but%20the%20physical%20assault%20went%20out%20of%20hand%2C%20resulting%20in%20their%20death.%20It%20was%20then%20they%20were%20advised%20by%20vigilantes%20to%20burn%20the%20bodies%20to%20destroy%20evidence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnasir-junaid-