ractor%20from%20Cheyenne%2C%20Wyo.%20told%20the%20media%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20at%20least%20six%2C%20seven%20feet%20or%20taller.%20It%20matched%20the%20sage%20in%20the%20mountains%20so%20much%20that%20he's%20like%20camouflaged%20when%20crouching%20down...if%20you%20asked%20before%20our%20trip%20we%20would%20have%20said%20maybe%20%5BBigfoot%5D%20could%20be%20real%2C%20but%20now%20we're%20convinced.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShannon%20Parker%20posted%20the%20video%20on%20Facebook%2C%20with%20the%20caption%2C%20%26quot%3BOn%20Sunday%2C%20October%208%2C%202023%2C%20Stetson%20Tyler%20and%20I%20took%20the%20Narrow%20Gauge%20train%20ride%20from%20Durango%20to%20Silverton.%20After%20leaving%20Silverton%20and%20heading%20back%20to%20Durango%2C%20I%20asked%20Stetson%20to%20help%20me%20look%20for%20elk%20in%20the%20mountains.%20As%20we%20are%20passing%20by%20the%20mountains%2C%20Stetson%20sees%20something%20moving%20and%20then%20says%20I%20think%20it's%20Bigfoot.%20Brandon%2C%20the%20guy%20sitting%20next%20to%20Stetson%20on%20the%20train%20grabs%20his%20phone%20and%20starts%20recording.%20Meanwhile%2C%20I%20am%20trying%20to%20get%20a%20photo%20on%20my%20camera.%20Below%20is%20the%20video%20Brandon%20%40bt92.travels%20got%20and%20the%20photos%20I%20took.%20Y'all%2C%20out%20of%20the%20hundreds%20of%20people%20on%20the%20train%2C%20three%20or%20four%20of%20us%20saw%2C%20as%20Stetson%20says%20in%20the%20video%2C%20the%20ever-elusive%20creature%20Bigfoot!%20I%20don't%20know%20about%20y'all%20but%20We%20Believe!!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20post%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fpost.php%3Fhref%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252Fshannon.law.37%252Fposts%252Fpfbid02ACcj1nmkuBqkMN8dCSnK1MgpcyqiJ6ynRxeJQiK1DvYgJ3FuHuDg5c9gmeBUstCol%26show_text%3Dtrue%26width%3D500%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22250%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20has%20gone%20viral%20and%20was%20posted%20on%20various%20social%20media%20platforms.%20The%20video%20amassed%20an%20array%20of%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20user%20commented%2C%20%26quot%3BThat's%20just%20a%20guy%20in%20a%20costume...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20user%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BBigfoot's%20existence%20has%20been%20known%20for%20years...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B2023%20and%20the%20couple%20doesn't%20know%20how%20to%20use%20the%20zoom%20feature%20on%20a%20camera%20probably%20didn't%20want%20people%20to%20see%20the%20zipper%20on%20the%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20third%20user%20commented.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%20it%20blended%20in%20with%20the%20grass%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20fourth%20user%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLooks%20right%20to%20me!%20How%20crazy%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20fifth%20user%20commented.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697090760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fn141drq_bigfoot_625x300_12_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fwatch-us-couple-spots-bizarre-creature-moving-through-woods-sparks-bigfoot-speculation-4473559%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20now-viral%20video%20sparked%20'Bigfoot'%20speculations%20and%20was%20captured%20by%20a%20couple%20who%20were%20on%20a%20romantic%20break%20in%20Colorado.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fwatch-us-couple-spots-bizarre-creature-moving-through-woods-sparks-bigfoot-speculation-4473559%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fwatch-us-couple-spots-bizarre-creature-moving-through-woods-sparks-bigfoot-speculation-4473559%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fwatch-us-couple-spots-bizarre-creature-moving-through-woods-sparks-bigfoot-speculation-44