d%20victimhood%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20here%20that%20a%20key%20bridge%20in%20the%20Hindutva-Zionist%20relationship%20becomes%20visible%3A%20a%20common%20cultural%20enemy.%20The%20Israeli%20state%E2%80%99s%20very%20founding%20was%20based%20on%20a%20direct%20military%20confrontation%20with%20Arab%20Muslim%20powers%20and%20displacement%20of%20Arab%2C%20mostly-Muslim%20Palestinians.%20This%20instantly%20made%20them%20a%20natural%20compadre%20for%20the%20Hindutvavadis%2C%20who%20have%20long%20marked%20out%20Muslims%20(and%20Islam)%20as%20the%20primary%20cultural%20threat%20to%20their%20imagined%20body%20politic.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20success%20of%20the%20Zionist%20forces%20in%20containing%20the%20%E2%80%9CMuslim%20threat%E2%80%9D%20through%20external%20military%20aggression%20and%20internal%20colonisation%20makes%20Israel%20the%20ideal%20reference%20point%20for%20the%20Hindutva-%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Evadis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20As%20Kaul%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgjia.georgetown.edu%2F2022%2F06%2F17%2Findia-israel-and-geopolitical-imaginaries-of-cooperation-and-oppression%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eobserves%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20right-wing%20majoritarian%20nationalist%20projects%20championed%20by%20the%C2%A0regimes%20in%20the%20two%20countries%C2%A0both%20portray%20themselves%20as%20beleaguered%20by%20Islamists%20and%20resolute%20in%20combating%20terrorism.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20again%2C%20we%20need%20not%20hunt%20for%20clues%20in%20the%20dense%20forest%2C%20for%20the%20evidence%20sits%20bare%20in%20the%20open%20field.%20Sample%20this%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2Fmumbai%2Fhinduism-and-judaism-should-come-together%2Farticle29263943.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estatement%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20made%20by%20senior%20BJP%20veteran%2C%20Subramaniam%20Swamy%2C%20during%20a%20joint%20panel%20discussion%20with%20Israeli%20academic%2C%20Gadi%20Taub%2C%20organised%20by%20the%20%E2%80%9CIndo-Israel%20Friendship%20Association%E2%80%9D%20in%20Mumbai%20in%20August%202019%3A%20%E2%80%9CZion%20is%20today%20under%20attack%20from%20Islamic%20extremists%2C%20and%20therefore%20both%20of%20us%20%5BHindutva-%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Evadis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20Zionists%5D%20should%20come%20together%20to%20fight%20the%20Islamic%20terror%20forces.%E2%80%9D%20This%20congruence%20of%20perceived%20victimhood%20to%20Islamist%20extremism%20is%20integral%20to%20both%20ideologies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20importantly%2C%20the%20pinpoint%20identification%20of%20a%20veritable%20common%20enemy%20logically%20segues%20into%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20legal-political%20system%20that%20marginalises%20that%20enemy.%20Thus%2C%20the%20adulatory%20Hindutva%20fascination%20for%20the%20Zionist%20project%20also%20extends%20to%20its%20desire%20to%20create%20a%20hierarchical%20citizenship%20structure%20within%20a%20Hindu%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERashtra%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20would%20privilege%20Hindus%20over%20other%20religious%20groups%2C%20especially%20Muslims.%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Basic%20Law%3A%20Israel%20as%20the%20Nation-State%20of%20the%20Jewish%20People%E2%80%99%20law%2C%20upheld%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202021%2C%20definitively%20establishes%20Israel%20as%20a%20homeland%20for%20Jews.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20academic%2C%20Honaida%20Ghanim%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fread.dukeupress.edu%2Fcritical-times%2Farticle%2F4%2F3%2F565%2F294168%2FIsrael-s-Nation-State-LawHierarchized-Citizenship%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eobserves%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20law%20also%20applies%20to%20Jews%20from%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20world%2C%20thus%20%E2%80%9C%5Breinventing%20citizenship%5D%20as%20a%20transboundary%20ethnos%20that%20automatically%20subsumes%20Jews%20from%20across%20the%20world%20into%20an%20ethnoracially%20engineered%20reserve%20of%20potential%20citizens.%E2%80%9D%20This%20is%20very%20close%20to%20what%20India%E2%80%99s%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%202019%2C%20which%20the%20BJP%20government%20put%20in%20place%20to%20regularise%20Hindu%20and%20five%20other%20non-Muslim%20immigrant%20groups%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20Afghanistan%2C%20seeks%20to%20achieve.%20The%20CAA%20iterates%20a%20certain%20breed%20of%20ethnoracial%20homelands%20politics%20that%20the%20Israeli%20%E2%80%98Basic%20Law%E2%80%99%20successfully%20institutionalised%20to%20a%20larger%20extent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENeither%20the%20Israeli%20%E2%80%98Basic%20Law%E2%80%99%2C%20nor%20the%20CAA%20(or%20even%20a%20proposed%20all-India%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens)%20are%20designed%20to%20physically%20expel%20the%20%E2%80%9Cundesirables%E2%80%9D.%20They%20are%20merely%20designed%20to%20establish%20a%20system%20of%20political%20and%20cultural%20majoritarianism%20by%20rendering%20dispensable%20groups%20into%20half-citizens%2C%20doubtful%20citizens%20or%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20non-citizens.%20In%20his%20book%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Biggest%20Prison%20on%20Earth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Pappe%20calls%20this%20unique%20formula%20of%20keeping%20the%20territories%2C%20not%20expelling%20the%20people%20in%20them%2C%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%20not%20granting%20them%20citizenship%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20unholy%20trinity%20of%20the%20consensual%20Zionist%20catechism.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EVicarious%20militarism%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFinally%2C%20the%20Hindutva%20ecosystem%E2%80%99s%20unmitigated%20fascination%20for%20the%20Israeli%20state%20and%20its%20actions%20cannot%20be%20understood%20without%20situating%20it%20in%20the%20contemporary%20context%20of%20the%20India-Israel%20bilateral%20relationship.%20Much%20has%20already%20been%20written%20about%20the%20renewed%20political%20and%20strategic%20cooperation%20between%20both%2C%20entailing%20strong%20interdependencies%20and%20investments%20in%20the%20defence%20and%20technological%20domains.%20As%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.middleeasteye.net%2Fnews%2Findia-israel-arms-trade-numbers%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMay%202022%20report%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20journalist%20and%20writer%2C%20Assad%20Essa%2C%20shows%2C%20military-to-military%20cooperation%20between%20both%20sides%20is%20at%20an%20all-time%20high%2C%20with%20India%20emerging%20as%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20top%20arms%20buyer%20and%20key%20co-production%20partner.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20of%20this%20is%20firmly%20backed%20by%20a%20longstanding%20legacy%20of%20deep%20state%20cooperation%2C%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20eagerness%20to%20lure%20India%20away%20from%20its%20neutral%20stance%20on%20the%20Palestine%20issue%2C%20and%20more%20recently%2C%20a%20shifting%20geopolitical%20context%20in%20West%20Asia%20that%20allows%20New%20Delhi%20to%20simultaneously%20consolidate%20its%20relationship%20with%20Tel%20Aviv%20and%20the%20Arab%20monarchies%20who%20are%20themselves%20warming%20up%20to%20Israel.%20The%20revamped%20political%20and%20military%20cooperation%2C%20however%2C%20is%20merely%20a%20material%20manifestation%20of%20the%20deeper%20ideological%20intimacy%20between%20two%20ethno-racially%20driven%20regimes.%20At%20best%2C%20it%20offers%20a%20visible%20platform%20for%20both%20to%20share%20their%20imaginaries%20of%20hyper-militaristic%20nationalism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20modern%20Hindutva%20elite%2C%20especially%2C%20which%20envisions%20India%20as%20an%20assertive%20regional%20and%20global%20military%20force%2C%20Israel%20offers%20critical%20inspiration.%20Here%20is%20a%20small%20state%20that%20has%20erected%20a%20near-impenetrable%20fortress%20buttressed%20by%20formidable%20systems%20of%