ng%20Israel%20for%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EApollo%20Global%20Management%20CEO%20Marc%20Rowan%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-ackman-harvard-release-names-students-blaming-israel-violence-hamas-2023-10%5C%22%3Elatest%20business%20leader%20to%20slam%20an%20Ivy%20League%20institution%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20not%20taking%20a%20stronger%20stance%20against%20what%20he%20called%20antisemitism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20private-equity%20billionaire%20wrote%20an%20op-ed%20for%20the%20student%20newspaper%20of%20his%20alma%20mater%2C%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania.%20The%20guest%20column%20hasn't%20yet%20been%20published%2C%20but%20was%20viewed%20in%20full%20by%20Insider.%20In%20it%2C%20he%20demanded%20that%20the%20school's%20president%2C%20Elizabeth%20Magill%2C%20and%20the%20chairman%20of%20its%20board%20of%20trustees%2C%20Scott%20Bok%2C%20both%20step%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20urged%20his%20fellow%20alumni%20to%20%26quot%3Bclose%20their%20checkbooks%26quot%3B%20until%20the%20university%20top%20brass%20resign.%20%26quot%3BJoin%20me%20and%20many%20others%20who%20love%20UPenn%20by%20sending%20UPenn%20%241%20in%20place%20of%20your%20normal%2C%20discretionary%20contribution%20so%20that%20no%20one%20misses%20the%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERowan's%20letter%20points%20to%20the%20Palestine%20Writes%20Literary%20Festival%2C%20which%20was%20hosted%20at%20the%20university%20last%20month%20and%20has%20been%20a%20lightening%20rod%20of%20controversy.%20The%20festival%20prompted%20more%20than%204%2C000%20people%2C%20including%20Rowan%2C%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fadl.salsalabs.org%2Fupenn%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esign%20an%20open%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Magill%2C%20saying%20that%20%26quot%3Bplatforming%20of%20outright%20antisemitism%20without%20denunciation%20from%20the%20university%20is%20unacceptable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20the%20university%20responded%2C%20saying%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpresident.upenn.edu%2Fcontent%2Fstatement-palestine-writes-literature-festival%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20unequivocally%20%E2%80%94%20and%20emphatically%20%E2%80%94%20condemn%20antisemitism%20as%20antithetical%20to%20our%20institutional%20values.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20university%2C%20we%20also%20fiercely%20support%20the%20free%20exchange%20of%20ideas%20as%20central%20to%20our%20educational%20mission%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20continued.%20%26quot%3BThis%20includes%20the%20expression%20of%20views%20that%20are%20controversial%20and%20even%20those%20that%20are%20incompatible%20with%20our%20institutional%20values.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-is-there-fighting-in-israel-and-what-caused-the-conflict-2023-10%5C%22%3Elight%20of%20the%20attack%20by%20Hamas%20on%20Israel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Rowan%20has%20said%20the%20response%20was%20not%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPresident%20Magill's%20allowing%20of%20UPenn's%20imprimatur%20to%20be%20associated%20with%20this%20conference%2C%20and%20her%20failure%20to%20condemn%20this%20hate-filled%20call%20for%20ethnic%20cleansing%2C%20normalized%20and%20legitimized%20violence%20that%20ranged%20from%20the%20targeting%20of%20Jewish%20students%20and%20spaces%20here%20at%20UPenn%20to%20the%20horrific%20attacks%20in%20Israel%2C%26quot%3B%20Rowan%20wrote%20in%20his%20op-ed%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPenn%20didn't%20directly%20respond%20to%20Rowan's%20letter%20in%20an%20emailed%20response%20to%20Insider%2C%20but%20a%20spokesman%20forwarded%20responses%20that%20university%20leaders%20had%20sent%20to%20the%20campus%20community%20after%20an%20antisemitic%20incident%20on%20campus%20and%20after%20Hamas's%20attack%20on%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOrg