0Day%20event%20ends%20at%20midnight%20PT%20tonight.%20For%20more%20great%20savings%2C%20check%20out%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fdeals%2Fbest-prime-day-deals-october-2023-day-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20Prime%20Day%20deals%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20all%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPC%20gaming%20setup%20buying%20advice%3Ch3%3EAre%20wireless%20accessories%20better%20or%20worse%20than%20wired%20accessories%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20might%20look%20at%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20picks%20in%20this%20article%20and%20cringe%20at%20their%20cables.%20Why%20not%20pick%20a%20wireless%20option%3F%20Well%2C%20here's%20a%20tip%20that%20gaming%20accessory%20companies%20won't%20tell%20you%3A%20Wireless%20accessories%20are%20almost%20never%20worth%20the%20price%20increase%20over%20wired%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWired%20accessories%20not%20only%20send%20signals%20faster%20and%20more%20consistently%2C%20but%20you%20also%20never%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20charging%20them%2C%20running%20out%20of%20power%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20game%2C%20or%20losing%20your%20Bluetooth%20connection.%20Wired%20headsets%20sound%20better%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20let's%20be%20honest%2C%20the%20tiny%20amount%20of%20movement%20freedom%20that%20the%20lack%20of%20wires%20gives%20you%20isn't%20worth%20the%20money.%20It's%20not%20like%20you're%20going%20to%20be%20carrying%20your%20mouse%20around%20the%20room%20with%20you%20while%20you%20play%20League%20%E2%80%94%20you'll%20be%20sitting%20in%20one%20spot%2C%20cussing%20out%20your%20teammates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWired%20accessories%20are%20objectively%20better%20than%20their%20overpriced%20wireless%20ones.%20I'll%20die%20on%20this%20hill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EIs%20Prime%20Day%20a%20good%20time%20to%20shop%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYes!%20Although%20the%20deals%20we%20find%20might%20not%20be%20the%20biggest%20discounts%20of%20the%20year%20%E2%80%94