d%20constructive%20manner%20for%20an%20early%20and%20mutually%20acceptable%20resolution%20of%20the%20remaining%20issues%20along%20the%20LAC%20in%20the%20Western%20Sector%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoth%20countries%20have%20been%20in%20a%20standoff%20in%20Eastern%20Ladakh%20since%20April-May%202020%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20hand-to-hand%20clash%20in%20Galwan%20Valley%20where%20at%20least%2024%20soldiers%20lost%20their%20lives.%20Subsequently%2C%20several%20rounds%20of%20negotiations%20have%20taken%20place%2C%20ultimately%20resulting%20in%20disengagement%20at%20approximately%20four%20critical%20points%20of%20contention.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20progress%20on%20the%20strategic%20areas%20of%20Depsang%20and%20Demchok.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChina%20insists%20that%20both%20these%20areas%20are%20legacy%20issues%20of%20the%20border%20boundary%20dispute%2C%20which%20India%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20agree.%20India%20has%20maintained%20that%20the%20standoff%20cannot%20be%20resolved%20until%20both%20armies%20disengage%20at%20these%20two%20specific%20points%2C%20and%20the%20customary%20patrolling%20boundaries%20in%20the%20region%20are%20re-established.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20sides%20agreed%20to%20%E2%80%9Cmaintain%20the%20momentum%20of%20dialogue%20and%20negotiations%20through%20the%20relevant%20military%20and%20diplomatic%20mechanisms%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20also%20committed%20to%20maintain%20peace%20and%20tranquility%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20the%20border%20areas%20in%20the%20interim%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20Indian%20press%20note%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20last%20round%20of%20Corp%20commanders%20meeting%20in%20August%2C%20there%20was%20a%20joint%20press%20release%20issued%20together%20by%20India%20and%20China%2C%20which%20didn%E2%80%99t%20happen%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%2019th%20round%20of%20talks%20had%20taken%20place%20a%20week%20before%20the%20BRICS%20summit%20at%20South%20Afri