que%20in%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20Sialkot%20district%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20October%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20took%20place%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20Wednesday%20as%20Latif%20and%20his%20brother%20were%20leaving%20the%20Noor%20Madina%20mosque%20in%20Daska%20town%20after%20prayers%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Foct%2F11%2Fmastermind-behind-pathankot-attack-shahid-latif-shot-dead-by-unidentified-assailants-in-pakistan-2622911.html%5C%22%3Enews%20agency%20PTI%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Three%20individuals%20on%20motorcycles%20opened%20fire%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20immediate%20deaths%20of%2053-year-old%20Latif%20and%20Haris%20Hashim.%20Another%20individual%20was%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20district%20police%20officer%20of%20Sialkot%2C%20Hasan%20Iqbal%20termed%20Latif%E2%80%99s%20killing%20as%20an%20act%20of%20%E2%80%9Cterrorism%20and%20target%20killing%E2%80%9D.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CShahid%20Latif%20had%20security%20threats.%20All%20the%20investigators%20are%20on%20the%20spot.%20Details%20will%20be%20shared%20with%20media%20soon.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EUPDATE%3A%3Cbr%3E%20District%20Police%20Officer%2C%20Sialkot%2C%20Hasan%20Iqbal%20has%20confirmed%20the%20killing%20of%20Shahid%20Latif%2C%20terming%20the%20incident%20as%20an%20act%20of%20%E2%80%9Cterrorism%20and%20target%20killing%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShahid%20Latif%20had%20security%20threats.%20All%20the%20investigators%20are%20on%20the%20spot.%20Details%20will%20be%20shared%20with%20media%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F3C3mpoMoP2%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F3C3mpoMoP2%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FuKcTqPs3WK%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FuKcTqPs3WK%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20The%20Khorasan%20Diary%20(%40khorasandiary)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkhorasandiary%2Fstatus%2F1712062090582938105%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2011%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELatif%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Bilal%20and%20Noor%20Al%20Din%2C%20was%20designated%20a%20terrorist%20in%20India%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20(UAPA)%20and%20served%20as%20the%20launching%20commander%20of%20Jaish-e-Mohammed%20in%20Sialkot.%20He%20was%20actively%20involved%20in%20the%20planning%2C%20facilitation%2C%20and%20execution%20of%20terror%20attacks%20in%20India%2C%20according%20to%20officials.%20Latif%20first%20entered%20Kashmir%20in%201993%20from%20Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20banned%20Harkat-ul-Ansar%20terror%20group.%20He%20was%20arrested%20a%20year%20later%20and%20incarcerated%20in%20the%20Kol%20Balwal%20jail%20in%20Jammu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20time%20in%20prison%2C%20it%20is%20believed%20that%20he%20was%20further%20radicalised%2C%20possibly%20by%20JeM%20chief%20Masood%20Azhar%2C%20who%20was%20also%20detained%20in%20the%20same%20facility%20until%20his%20release%20in%201999%20as%20part%20of%20the%20exchange%20for%20the%20hostages%20of%20the%20Indian%20Airlines%20plane%20that%20was%20hijacked%20and%20taken%20to%20Kandahar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20serving%2016%20years%2C%20Latif%20was%20deported%20through%20the%20Attari-Wagah%20border%20in%202010%20and%20subsequently%20reconnected%20with%20Azhar%2C%20who%20had%20by%20then%20established%20the%20JeM.%20An%20unidentified%20official%20told%20PTI%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20the%20biggest%20blow%20to%20JeM%20on%20Pakistani%20soil.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fquestions-we-must-ask-about-the-pathankot-attack%5C%22%3E2016%20attack%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20Pathankot%20Air%20Force%20Station%20resulted%20in%20the%20death%20of%20seven%20IAF%20personnel%20and%20a%20three-day-long%20siege.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2