t%20the%20invitation%20of%20President%20William%20Ruto%20and%20ahead%20of%20Kenya's%2060th%20anniversary%20of%20independence%20from%20Britain.%20The%20trip%20will%20also%20acknowledge%20the%20painful%20aspects%20of%20the%20UK%20and%20Kenya's%20shared%20history%2C%20including%20the%20Mau%20Mau%20revolt.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fbritains-king-charles-to-pay-state-visit-to-kenya%2Farticleshow%2F104349821.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fbritains-king-charles-to-pay-state-visit-to-kenya%2Famp_articleshow%2F104349821.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fbritains-king-charles-to-pay-state-visit-to-kenya%2Famp_articleshow%2F104349821.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SC%20Declines%20to%20Grant%20Divorce%20to%20Couple%20in%2080s%20on%20Basis%20of%20Irretrievable%20Breakdown%20of%20Marriage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F14165452%2Fdivorce-619195_1280.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EA%20five-judge%20constitution%20bench%20had%20on%20May%201%20held%20in%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F37623680%2F%5C%22%3EShilpa%20Shailesh%20vs%20Varun%20Sreenivasan%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20the%20grant%20of%20divorce%20on%20the%20ground%20of%20irretrievable%20breakdown%20of%20marriage%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20not%20a%20matter%20of%20right%2C%20but%20a%20discretion%20which%20is%20to%20be%20exercised%20with%20great%20care%20and%20caution.%20The%20court%20had%20declared%20that%20it%20had%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20several%20factors%20ensuring%20that%20%E2%80%98complete%20justice%E2%80%99%20is%20done%20to%20both%20parties.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%20also%20held%20that%20it%20should%20be%20fully%20convinced%20and%20satisfied%20that%20the%20marriage%20is%20totally%20unworkable%2C%20emotionally%20dead%20and%20beyond%20salvation%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20dissolution%20of%20marriage%20is%20the%20right%20solution%20and%20the%20only%20way%20forward.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20court%20held%20that%20it%20has%20to%20factually%20determine%20and%20firmly%20establish%20that%20the%20marriage%20has%20irretrievably%20broken%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20this%2C%20the%20court%20ought%20to%20consider%20several%20factors%20such%20as%20the%20period%20of%20time%20the%20parties%20had%20cohabitation%20after%20marriage%3B%20when%20the%20parties%20had%20last%20cohabited%3B%20the%20nature%20of%20allegations%20made%20by%20the%20parties%20against%20each%20other%20and%20their%20family%20members%3B%20the%20orders%20passed%20in%20the%20legal%20proceedings%20from%20time%20to%20time%3B%20cumulative%20impact%20on%20the%20personal%20relationship%3B%20whether%2C%20and%20how%20many%20attempts%20were%20made%20to%20settle%20the%20disputes%20by%20intervention%20of%20the%20court%20through%20mediation%3B%20and%20when%20the%20last%20attempt%20was%20made%2C%20etc.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20importantly%2C%20the%20period%20of%20separation%20should%20be%20sufficiently%20long%2C%20and%20anything%20above%20six%20years%20or%20more%20will%20be%20a%20relevant%20factor%2C%20it%20had%20held.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20court%2C%20however%2C%20had%20refrained%20from%20codifying%20the%20factors%20so%20as%20not%20to%20curtail%20the%20exercise%20of%20jurisdiction%20under%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F500307%2F%5C%22%3EArticle%20142(1)%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%2C%20which%20it%20held%2C%20is%20situation%20specific.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20%3Ci%3EShilpa%20Shailesh%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20the%20bench%20did%20not%20have%20to%20deal%20with%20a%20situation%20in%20which%20one%20of%20the%20parties%20opposed%20the%20dissolution%20of%20marriage%2C%20despite%20living%20separately%20for%20many%20years.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20October%2010%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Aniriddha%20Bose%20and%20Bela%20M.%20Trivedi%2C%20had%20to%20deal%20with%20a%20case%20in%20which%20it%20was%20satisfied%20that%20there%20was%20an%20irretrievable%20breakdown%20of%20marriage%20between%20the%20couple%2C%20but%20one%20of%20the%20spouses%20opposed%20the%20prayer%20for%20dissolution%20of%20marriage.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20wife%2C%20who%20is%2082%20years%20old%2C%20was%20willing%20to%20tend%20to%20her%20husband%2C%20who%20is%2089%2C%20despite%20living%20separately%20for%20several%20years.%20The%20wife%20had%20taken%20care%20of%20her%20three%20children%20since%201963%2C%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20appellant-husband%20had%20exhibited%20total%20hostility%20towards%20them.%20She%20is%20still%20ready%20and%20willing%20to%20take%20care%20of%20her%20husband%20and%20does%20not%20wish%20to%20leave%20him%20alone%20at%20this%20stage%20of%20life%2C%20the%20bench%20noted.%20She%20also%20expressed%20her%20sentiments%20that%20she%20does%20not%20want%20to%20die%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98stigma%E2%80%99%20of%20being%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdivorcee%E2%80%9D%20woman.%20%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIn%20defence%20of%20marriage%20as%20an%20institution%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20agreed%20that%20in%20contemporary%20society%2C%20divorce%20may%20not%20constitute%20stigma%2C%20but%20did%20not%20want%20to%20ignore%20her%20sentiment.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20bench%20concluded%20that%20dissolving%20the%20marriage%20between%20the%20parties%20on%20the%20ground%20of%20irretrievable%20breakdown%20of%20marriage%20would%20not%20be%20doing%20%E2%80%9Ccomplete%20justice%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20parties%2C%20but%20would%20rather%20be%20doing%20injustice%20to%20the%20respondent-wife.%20The%20bench%2C%20therefore%2C%20dismissed%20the%20appeal%20of%20the%20husband%20against%20the%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20dissolve%20the%20marriage.%20%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20observed%20that%20the%20institution%20of%20marriage%20occupies%20an%20important%20place%20and%20plays%20an%20important%20role%20in%20society.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3EDespite%20the%20increasing%20trend%20of%20filing%20divorce%20proceedings%20in%20courts%20of%20law%2C%20the%20institution%20of%20marriage%20is%20still%20considered%20to%20be%20a%20pious%2C%20spiritual%20and%20invaluable%20emotional%20life%20net%20between%20the%20husband%20and%20the%20wife%20in%20Indian%20society%2C%20the%20bench%20added.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3EIt%20is%20governed%20not%20only%20by%20the%20letters%20of%20law%20but%20by%20the%20social%20norms%20as%20well%3B%20so%20many%20other%20relationships%20stem%20from%20and%20thrive%20on%20the%20matrimonial%20relationships%20in%20the%20society%2C%20the%20bench%20noted.%20%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20above%20observations%20are%20significant%2C%20especially%20as%20a%20constitution%20bench%20of%20the%20apex%20court%20is%20expected%20to%20give%20its%20verdict%20in%20the%20case%20involving%20the%20right%20of%20same-sex%20couple%20to%20marry.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20Union%20of%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Funion-government-opposes-same-sex-marriages-in-supreme-court%23%3A~%3Atext%3Dlaw-%2CUnion%2520Government%2520Opposes%2520Same%252DSex%2520Marriages%2520in%2520Supreme%2520Court%2Cthe%2520Union%2520government%2520has%2520said.%5C%22%3Eopposed%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20petition%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20it%20is%20against%20the%20institution%20of%20marriage%2C%20which%20it%20claimed%2C%20is%20heterosexual.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20it%20would%20not%20be%20desirable%20to%20accept%20the%20formula%20of%20%E2%80%9Cirretrievable%20breakdown%20of%20marriage%E2%80%9D%20as%20a%20straitjacket%20formula%20for%20the%20grant%20of%20relief%20of%20divorce%20under%20Article%20142%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20the%20bench%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmain.sci.gov.in%2Fsupremecourt%2F2009%2F13430%2F13430_2009_6_1501_47544_Judgement_10-Oct-2023.pdf%5C%22%3Econcluded%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20instant%20case%2C%20the%20bench%20agreed%20that%20there%20is%20no%20dispute%20that%20the%20parties%20have%20been%20separated%20for%20many%20years%20and%20all%20efforts%20to%20bring%20them%20together%20had%20failed.%20Under%20the%20circumstances%2C%20one%20may%20presume%20that%20the%20marriage%20is%20emotionally%20dead%20and%20beyond%20salvation%20and%20that%20there%20is%20an%20irretrievable%20breakdown%20of%20marriage%20between%20the%20parties.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20judgment%2C%20authored%20by%20Justice%20Trivedi%2C%20had%20also%20concluded%20that%20the%20appellant-husband%20had%20failed%20to%20prove%20that%20the%20respondent-wife%20had%20treated%20him%20with%20%E2%80%9Ccruelty%E2%80%9D%20or%20that%20she%20had%20%E2%80%9Cdeserted%E2%80%9D%20him%20as%20contemplated%20in%20Section%2013(1)(ia)%20and%2013(1)(ib)%20respectively%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Marriage%20Act%2C%201955.%20The%20Chandigarh%20district%20court%20had%20accepted%20the%20husband%E2%80%99s%20contention%20and%20granted%20him%20a%20divorce%2C%20which%20was%20reversed%20by%20both%20the%20single%20judge%20and%20the%20division%20bench%20of%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697039056000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F14165452%2Fdivorce-619195_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-divorce-irretrievable-breakdown-of-marriage%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20court%20took%20note%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20while%20the%20husband%2C%20who%20is%C2%A087%20years%20old%2C%20sought%20divorce%2C%20the%20wife%2C%2082%2C%20did%20not.%C2%A0Though%20they%20had%20been%20living%20separately%20for%20many%20years%2C%20the%20woman%20said%20she%20does%20not%20want%20to%20die%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98stigma%E2%80%99%20of%20being%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdivorcee%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-divorce-irretrievable-breakdown-of-marriage%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20could%20launch%20ground%20attack%20against%20Hamas%20'in%20hours'%20-%20but%20what%20would%20it%20look%20like%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697038560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F1600x900%2Fskynews-israel-hamas-war-gaza_6317818.jpg%3F20231011112910%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fisrael-could-launch-ground-attack-against-hamas-in-hours-or-days-but-what-would-it-look-like-12982591%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israel%20could%20be%20just%20%26quot%3Bhours%20or%20days%26quot%3B%20from%20launching%20a%20ground%20offensive%20against%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza%2C%20according%20to%20Sky's%C2%A0security%20and%20defence%20analyst%20Michael%20Clarke.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A404%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fisrael-could-launch-ground-attack-against-hamas-in-hours-or-days-but-what-would-it-look-like-12982591%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fisrael-could-launch-ground-attack-against-hamas-in-hours-or-days-but-what-would-it-look-like-12982591%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fisrael-could-launch-ground-attack-against-hamas-in-hours-or-days-but-what-would-it-look-like-12982591%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20confirmed%20figure%20on%20kibbutz%20baby%20deaths%3A%20Israeli%20foreign%20ministry%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697