uring%20states.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%20promote%20local%20and%20organic%20produce.%20Second%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20tackling%20the%20issue%20of%20plastic%20and%20dry%20waste.%20Around%2080%20percent%20of%20our%20household%20dry%20waste%2C%20such%20as%20plastic%2C%20glass%2C%20and%20paper%2C%20comes%20from%20our%20kitchens%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Khandelwal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Sensible%20Earth%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326377%2Fnoida-madhuri-balodi-amit-singh-kavi-the-poetry-art-project-glass-bottle-art-sustainability-home-decor%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eactively%20collecting%20glass%20jars%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20having%20already%20collected%202%2C000%20with%20a%20target%20of%20reaching%2010%2C000.%20Khandelwal%20points%20out%20that%20recycling%20glass%20can%20have%20a%20higher%20environmental%20impact%2C%20so%2C%20they%20have%20launched%20a%20campaign%20to%20collect%2C%20clean%2C%20and%20store%20glass%20jars%20in%20collaboration%20with%20local%20self-help%20groups.%20They%20are%20now%20exploring%20ways%20to%20repurpose%20these%20jars%20within%20Goa%E2%80%99s%20food%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKhandelwal%20maintains%20that%20this%20battle%20with%20plastic%20or%20waste%2C%20in%20general%2C%20is%20a%20long-drawn%20affair%2C%20and%20there%20is%20an%20ongoing%20need%20to%20raise%20awareness.%20He%20highlights%20the%20importance%20of%20changing%20the%20perception%20of%20Goa%2C%20which%20is%20often%20solely%20associated%20with%20fun%20and%20enjoyment.%20This%20perception%20puts%20tremendous%20pressure%20on%20waste%20management%20and%20the%20environment%2C%20especially%20considering%20the%20fact%20that%20Goa%20receives%20four%20times%20more%20tourists%20than%20its%20actual%20population%20(15%20lakhs).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20change%20the%20narrative%20of%20tourism%20in%20Goa.%20It%20is%20a%20biodiversity%20hotspot%2C%20an%20extremely%20fragile%20ecosystem%2C%20and%20one%20has%20to%20walk%20carefully%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Khandelwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWritten%20by%20Arti%20Das%3B%20All%20photos%20courtesy%20Arti%20Das.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcpcb.nic.in%2Fuploads%2Fplasticwaste%2FAnnual_Report_2019-20_PWM.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnnual%20Report%202019-20%20on%20Implementation%20of%20Plastic%20Waste%20Management%20Rules%2C%202016%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%20by%20Central%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20Delhi%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.heraldgoa.in%2FGoa%2FGoa-tops-in-per-capita-plastic-waste-generation%2F181114%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520report%2520states%2520that%2520Goa%2Cis%2520approximately%252015%2520lakh%2520persons%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoa%20tops%20in%20per%20capita%20plastic%20waste%20generation%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%20by%20O%20Heraldo%2C%20Published%20on%2010%20October%2C%202021.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.financialexpress.com%2Flife%2Ftravel-tourism-goa-is-expecting-to-welcome-81-lakh-tourists-on-par-with-pre-pandemic-time-2911390%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoa%20is%20expecting%20to%20welcome%2081%20lakh%20tourists%2C%20on%20par%20with%20pre-pandemic%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%20by%20Financial%20Express%2C%20Published%20on%2013%20December%2C%202022.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697030936000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.theb