20Bihar%20where%20I%C2%A0%20grew%20up%20witnessed%20girls%20my%20age%20being%20married%20right%20after%20Class%2010.%20It%20was%20customary%20for%20fathers%20to%20set%20aside%20money%20for%20their%20dowry.%20But%2C%20I%20had%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331323%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-2023-nari-shakti-vandan-adhiniyam-pramila-dandavate-modi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edifferent%20dreams%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20so%20my%20father%20invested%20that%20same%20money%20into%20my%20education.%20Things%20were%20not%20always%20easy%20as%20we%20lived%20in%20a%20%3Cem%3Ekaccha%20%3C%2Fem%3E(makeshift)%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehouse.%20My%20father%20would%20repair%20gas%20stoves%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%20But%20even%20when%20finances%20were%20low%20he%20ensured%20I%20studied.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThough%20my%20family%20was%20supportive%20of%20my%20dreams%2C%20there%20was%20another%20challenge%20to%20deal%20with%20%E2%80%94%20relatives.%20Right%20from%20telling%20my%20father%20he%20was%20wasting%20money%20on%20my%20education%20to%20advising%20him%20to%20marry%20me%20off%2C%20they%20tried%20their%20best%20to%20discourage%20him.%20They%20even%20tried%20forcing%20me%20to%20cook%20and%20be%20like%20the%20other%20girls%20they%20knew%2C%20but%20my%20dad%20became%20my%20shield%20against%20these%20taunts%20and%20pressure.%20And%20that%E2%80%99s%20how%20I%20grew%20up%20protected%20from%20the%20outside%20world.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20in%20later%20years%20I%20began%20to%20appreciate%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331721%2Frajasthan-government-school-teacher-trains-self-defense-to-girls-with-disabilities-national-award%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20side%20of%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20always.%20In%20school%2C%20I%20remember%20writing%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EBauji%3C%2Fem%3E%20(father)%