0%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Aaquib%20said%20his%20first%20step%20was%20to%20refer%20to%20textile%20designer%20Aditi%20Ranjan%E2%80%99s%20book%20%E2%80%98Handmade%20in%20India%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20from%20here%20that%20I%20made%20a%20depository%20of%20motifs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%20%E2%80%9CI%20got%20%3Cem%3Ebagh%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20%3Cem%3Emarapani%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewood%20carving%20from%20Kerala%2C%20bamboo%20basketry%20from%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Nagaland%20skirt%20patterns%2C%20Misoram%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Ekwapusial%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Etelia%20rumal%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Ladakhi%20%3Cem%3Epsug%20dgan%3C%2Fem%3E%20rugs.%20I%20also%20got%20paintings%20applique%20from%20Madurai%2C%20%3Cem%3Egamucha%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20Assam%2C%20Sanchi%20paper%20cut%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20paper%20m%C3%A2ch%C3%A9%20from%20Kashmir%2C%20motifs%20in%20Tibetan%20carpets%E2%80%A6%20and%20the%20list%20goes%20on!%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAaquib%20further%20shared%20that%20while%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20%E2%80%9Ctrying%20to%20be%20a%20torchbearer%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F321283%2Fjodhpur-kavad-artisan-satyanarayan-suthar-revives-centuries-old-rajasthan-traditional-art%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20handicrafts%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20wanted%20to%20uphold%20the%20idea%20of%20giving%20an%20apt%20representation%20of%20our%20rich%20history.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20work%20was%20commended%20by%20Parth%20Jindal%2C%20founder%20and%20director%20of%20JSW%20Sports%2C%20who%20spoke%20of%20how%20Aaquib%E2%80%99s%20work%20was%20a%20feather%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20cap.%20%E2%80%9COver%20the%20years%2C%20India%20has%20made%20immense%20strides%20in%20the%20field%20of%20sports%2C%20and%20now%20the%20whole%20world%20is%20looking%20at%20us%20as%20a%20force%20to%20reckon%20with.%20It%20has